iciary%2C%20according%20to%20you...%20(but)%20that%20party%20is%20still%20not%20made%20an%20accused%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20bench%20of%20Justice%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%20and%20Justice%20SV%20Bhatti%20said%20yesterday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-liquor-policy-case-supreme-court-manish-sisodia-if-aap-benefited-why-isnt-it-accused-supreme-courts-liquor-case-query-4449082%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BIf%20AAP%20Benefited%2C%20Why%20Isn't%20It%20Accused%26quot%3B%3A%20Supreme%20Court's%20Query%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESources%20have%20told%20NDTV%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20has%20a%20money%20trail%20leading%20to%20the%20AAP%20-%20a%20cache%20of%20evidence%2C%20the%20agency%20believes%2C%20proves%20the%20cash%20was%20used%20to%20fund%20election%20campaigns.%20The%20agency%20is%20exploring%20legal%20opinions%20on%20making%20the%20AAP%20an%20accused.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20had%20also%20raised%20a%20second%20%26quot%3Blegal%20question%26quot%3B%20on%20Wednesday%20-%20if%20a%20cabinet%20note%20(specifically%2C%20Delhi%20government%20notes%20on%20the%20formation%20of%20the%20liquor%20policy)%20can%20be%20examined%20by%20a%20court%20of%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20believe%20there%20are%20specific%20Constitution%20bench%20judgments%20barring%20us%20from%20examining%20cabinet%20notes.%20I%20do%20not%20know%20if%20it%20applies%20to%20Delhi...%20because%20it%20is%20a%20Union%20Territory.%20(It%20is)%20like%20the%20issue%20of%20how%20we%20cannot%20get%20into%20what%20is%20said%20in%20Parliament...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Sisodia%2C%20then%20also%20the%20Delhi%20government's%20excise%20commissioner%2C%20is%20the%20prime%20accused%20in%20the%20liquor%20policy%20scam%3B%20investigating%20agencies%20have%20referred%20to%20him%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bkingpin%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bmastermind%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20