.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fexplainer-why-donald-trump-cant-become-us-house-speaker-for-now%2Famp_articleshow%2F104181190.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fexplainer-why-donald-trump-cant-become-us-house-speaker-for-now%2Famp_articleshow%2F104181190.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Airbnb%20Guest%20Living%20Rent%20Free%20At%20US%20Mansion%20Wants%20Landlord%20To%20Pay%20%24100%2C000%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAn%20Airbnb%20guest%20has%20been%20staying%20in%20a%20luxury%20Los%20Angeles%20mansion%20for%20more%20than%20a%20year%20and%20is%20refusing%20to%20leave%20unless%20the%20landlord%20pays%20her%20a%20%24100%2C000%20relocation%20fee%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.latimes.com%2Fcalifornia%2Fstory%2F2023-10-04%2Fairbnb-guest-refuse-pay-leave-luxury-rental%5C%22%3ELos%20Angeles%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20media%20outlet%2C%20Aleksandar%20Jovanovic%2C%20an%20internationally%20celebrated%20periodontist%20rented%20out%20the%20mansion%20to%20Elizabeth%20Hirschhorn%20back%20in%20September%202021.%20She%20rented%20the%20house%20for%20six%20months%20at%20a%20rate%20of%20%24105%20a%20night%2C%20with%20fees%20bringing%20the%20total%20to%20%2420%2C793%2C%20according%20to%20court%20documents.%20However%2C%20her%20stay%20ended%20in%20April%202022%20and%20she%20has%20been%20staying%20there%20rent-free%20ever%20since.%20Mr%20Jovanovic%20is%20fearful%20for%20his%20and%20his%20family's%20safety.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20can%20never%20go%20into%20my%20home%20and%20know%20that%20I'm%20safe%20when%20a%20potentially%20hostile%20person%20is%20living%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20landlord%20told%20The%20Los%20Angeles%20Times.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20thinking%20about%20it%20at%20all%20times.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20judge%20recently%20ruled%20that%20the%20squatter%20can%20stay%20for%20as%20long%20as%20she%20likes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Jovanovic%20is%20struggling%20to%20kick%20the%20tenant%20out%20because%20his%20guest%20house%20was%20not%20supposed%20to%20be%20rented.%20He%20rented%20the%20house%20without%20a%20certificate%20of%20occupancy%20or%20proper%20registration.%20It%20also%20has%20a%20shower%20installed%20illegally%20in%20the%20unit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMs%20Hirschhorn's%20attorney%20in%20an%20email%20told%20LA%20Times%20argued%20that%20%26quot%3B%24100%2C000%20is%20%5BJovanovic's%5D%20cheapest%20way%20of%20getting%20off%20the%20whole%20ordeal.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20the%20home%20of%20the%20tenant%20until%20the%20landlord%20gets%20a%20judgment%2C%20however%20distasteful%20that%20is%20to%20your%20client.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20landlord%20broke%20the%20law%20and%20tried%20to%20make%20money%20by%20renting%20out%20an%20illegal%20bootleg%20unit%2C%26quot%3B%20her%20attorney%2C%20Colin%20Walshok%20told%20the%20LA%20Times.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20he%20was%20caught%2C%20instead%20of%20doing%20the%20right%20thing%2C%20he%20has%20resorted%20to%20bullying%2C%20harassment%20and%20the%20filing%20of%20frivolous%20lawsuits%20containing%20elaborate%20false%20stories%2C%20all%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20cover%20his%20tracks.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Jovanovic's%20lawyer%20Sebastian%20Rucci%20said%20that%20she's%20the%20tenant%20from%20hell.%20%26quot%3BIf%20she's%20right%2C%20the%20theory%20is%20that%20if%20a%20landlord%20has%20something%20that%20isn't%20permitted%2C%20then%20you%20can%20stay%20in%20it%20rent-free%20forever.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20early%20days%20were%20pleasant%2C%20Mr.%20Jovanovic%20told%20the%20LA%20Times.%20They%20exchanged%20niceties%20when%20their%20paths%20crossed%2C%20and%20they%20shared%20tea%20and%20small%20talk%20on%20the%20deck%20that%20separates%20the%20main%20house%20and%20ADU.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20lawsuit%2C%20the%20tension%20began%20about%20five%20months%20in%2C%20when%20Hirschhorn%20said%20her%20electronic%20blinds%20stopped%20working.%20When%20Mr%20Jovanovic%20went%20in%20to%20repair%20them%2C%20he%20noticed%20water%20damage%20and%20signs%20of%20mould%20around%20the%20sink%2C%20which%20he%20said%20weren't%20there%20before%20her%20stay.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20offered%20to%20pay%20her%20to%20stay%20at%20a%20hotel%20for%20five%20days%2C%20but%20she%20refused.%20He%20even%20offered%20her%20to%20stay%20at%20his%20house%2C%20but%20she%20declined%20that%20as%20well%2C%20citing%20an%20extreme%20disability%20due%20to%20cat%20dander.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20claims%20in%20a%20countersuit%20that%20he%20%26quot%3Binappropriately%20invited%26quot%3B%20her%20to%20move%20in%20with%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20tension%20lasted%20through%20the%20end%20of%20her%20stay%20till%20the%20end%20of%20March%202022.%20When%20it%20became%20clear%20to%20Mr.%20Jovanovic%20that%20she%20wasn't%20leaving%2C%20he%20allowed%20her%20to%20stay%20till%20April%2012%20so%20she%20could%20find%20another%20place.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20asked%20for%20more%20time%2C%20but%20I%20told%20her%20it%20wasn't%20possible%20since%20I%20had%20other%20Airbnb%20reservations%20coming%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20then%20I%20tried%20to%20be%20nice%20and%20give%20her%20an%20extra%20few%20weeks.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Jovanovic%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20city's%20Department%20of%20Building%20Safety%20because%20she%20refused%20to%20move.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20then%20sent%20a%20complaint%20to%20a%20housing%20investigator%2C%20alleging%20illegal%20eviction%2C%20harassment%20and%20a%20refusal%20to%20pay%20her%20relocation%20fees.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20housing%20investigator%20said%20that%20the%20unit%20violated%20city%20codes.%20And%20Mr%20Jovanovic%20should%20withdraw%20his%20eviction%20notice%20until%20he%20can%20prove%20the%20guest%20house%20was%20in%20