icleshow%2F104179772.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Asian%20Games%3A%20How%20India%20Can%20Win%20100%20Medals%2C%20Fulfil%3B%20'Sau%20Paar'%20Prophecy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20contingent%20recorded%20its%20biggest-ever%20medal%20haul%20in%20the%20history%20of%20Asian%20Games%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20as%20it%20went%20past%20the%2070%20mark%20at%20the%20Hangzhou%20event.%20As%20the%20sporting%20world%20lauded%20the%20Indian%20athletes%20in%20China%20for%20their%20stupendous%20effort%2C%20many%20reminded%20them%20that%20the%20job%20wasn't%20yet%20done.%20The%20target%20for%20the%20Indian%20contingent%20has%20been%20going%20past%20the%20100-medal%20mark%20in%20the%202022%20Asian%20Games%2C%20and%20with%20four%20days%20to%20go%20before%20the%20event%20concludes%2C%20there's%20every%20possibility%20of%20that%20happening.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHaving%20already%20won%2083%20medals%2C%20including%20the%20archery%20women's%20team%20gold%20medal%20and%20mixed%20doubles%20squash%20gold%20that%20came%20on%20Thursday%2C%20India%20need%2017%20more%20medals%20to%20touch%20the%20100-medal%20mark.%20If%20things%20go%20as%20planned%20over%20the%20remaining%20days%2C%20the%20overall%20medals%20tally%20would%20go%20past%20the%20century%20mark.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHow%20India%20can%20go%20past%20the%20100-medal%20mark%20in%20Hangzhou%20Asian%20Games%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESquash%3A%201%20Medal%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%20won%20the%20gold%20medal%20in%20the%20mixed%20doubles%20event%20after%20Dipika%20Pallikal%20and%20Harinder%20Pal%20Singh%20Sandhu%20defeated%20the%20Malaysian%20pair.%20India%20are%20assured%20of%20another%20medal%20in%20squash%2C%20having%20reached%20the%20men's%20singles%20final.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWrestling%3A%206%20Medals%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFreestyle%20wrestling%20is%20where%20India%20are%20at%20their%20strongest%20in%20the%20sport.%20With%20Antim%20Panghal%2C%20Pooja%20Gehlot%20participating%2C%20Ind