no%20doctor%20attended%20to%20the%20newborn%2C%20the%20complainant%20has%20alleged.%20When%20they%20went%20to%20the%20dean's%20office%20for%20help%2C%20they%20were%20driven%20away%2C%20the%20complaint%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20comes%20a%20day%20after%20the%20dean%20filed%20a%20police%20complaint%20against%20an%20MP%20of%20the%20ruling%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%20who%20made%20him%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fcities%2Fcase-against-shiv-sena-mp-hemant-patil-after-he-makes-nanded-hospital-dean-clean-toilet-4447998%5C%22%3Eclean%20a%20filthy%20toilet%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20hospital%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHemant%20Patil%2C%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP%20from%20Nanded%2C%20visited%20the%20Dr%20Shankarrao%20Chavan%20Government%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital%20on%20Tuesday%20after%20it%20made%20headlines%20with%2031%20deaths%20in%2072%20hours.%20These%20dead%20included%2016%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20visit%2C%20the%20MP%20told%20the%20media%20that%20he%20was%20pained%20to%20see%20the%20state%20of%20the%20toilets%20in%20the%20hospital.%20%26quot%3BThe%20government%20spends%20crores%2C%20but%20I%20am%20pained%20to%20see%20the%20situation%20here.%20The%20toilets%20have%20not%20been%20cleaned%20for%20months.%20The%20toilets%20in%20the%20wards%20of%20the%20hospital%20are%20locked.%20No%20water%20is%20available%20in%20toilets%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Patil%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20news%20agency%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFollowing%20Mr%20Wakode's%20complaint%2C%20Mr%20Patil%20was%20charged%20with%20IPC%20provisions%20relating%20to%20criminal%20force%20to%20deter%20a%20public%20servant%20from%20doing%20his%20duty%2C%20defamation%20and%20criminal%20intimidation.%20The%20MP%20was%20also%20charged%20under%20relevant%20provisions%20of%20the%20Scheduled%20Castes%20and%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20(Prevention%20of%20Atrocities)%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20hospital's%20dean%20had%20said%20in%20his%20complaint%20that%20the%20MP's%20conduct