0us%20some%20insights%20of%20what%20her%20relationship%20is%20like%20with%20her%20husband%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fsearch%3Fsearchtext%3DRishi-Sunak%5C%22%3ERishi%20Sunak%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMs%20Murty%20in%20her%20surprise%20speech%20on%20Wednesday%20stepped%20out%20to%20introduce%20%26quot%3Bbest%20friend%26quot%3B%20Rishi%20Sunak%20for%20his%20maiden%20speech%20as%20UK%20Prime%20Minister%20to%20the%20Conservative%20Party%20conference%20in%20Manchester.%20She%20during%20her%20light-hearted%20and%20personal%20speech%2C%20claimed%20her%20husband%20was%20unaware%20of%20her%20%26quot%3Bgate-crashing%26quot%3B%20as%20the%20warm-up%20act%20to%20the%20centrepiece%20of%20the%20annual%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FMxVq917y-L0%3Fsi%3DoJ_ju5jx1XP6d212%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22650%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22400%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere%20are%20some%20of%20the%20quotes%20from%20Akshata%20Murty%20's%20speech%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20are%20best%20friends%2C%20one%20team%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRishi%20and%20I%20are%20each%20other's%20best%20friends%3B%20we%20are%20one%20team%20and%20I%20could%20not%20imagine%20being%20anywhere%20else%20than%20here%20today%20to%20show%20my%20support%20to%20him%20and%20to%20the%20party%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStruck%20by%20two%20things%20about%20him%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRishi%20and%20I%20met%20when%20we%20were%2024%20when%20we%20were%20both%20studying%20abroad%20in%20America.%20Right%20from%20the%20very%20beginning%2C%20I%20was%20struck%20by%20two%20things%20about%20him...%20his%20deep%20love%20for%20his%20home%2C%20the%20United%20Kingdom%2C%20and%20his%20sincere%20desire%20to%20ensure%20as%20many%20people%20as%20possible%20have%20a%20chance%20to%20have%20the%20opportunities%20he%20was%20lucky%20enough%20to%20have%20had.%20It%20completely%20energised%20him.%20Being%20with%20Rishi%20was%20the%20easiest%20decision%20of%20my%20life%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDuring%20tough%20times%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSometimes%20when%20the%20going%20gets%20tough%2C%20I%20remind%20Rishi%20that%20he's%20fighting%20for%20his%20values.%20That%20he's%20fighting%20for%20this%20party's%20values%2C%20knowing%20that%20it's%20a%20hard%20road%20ahead.%20That%20success%20is%20hard%20one%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHis%20incredible%20zest%20for%20life%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20has%20an%20incredible%20zest%20for%20life.%20What%20drew%20me%20to%20him%20most%20was%20his%20strength%20of%20character%2C%20his%20honesty%2C%20his%20integrity%2C%20with%20a%20firm%20understanding%20of%20right%20from%20wrong.%20It's%20what%20I'm%20still%20drawn%20to%2C%20even%20today%2C%20after%2014%20years%20of%20being%20married.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20proud%20wife%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRishi%2C%20you%20know%20this%2C%20you%20know%20that%20doing%20the%20right%20thing%20for%20the%20long%20term%20even%20when%20it%20is%20hard%20is%20the%20right%20thing%20to%20do.%20I%20hope%20you%20also%20know%20how%20proud%20you%20make%20our%20girls%20and%20me%20every%20single%20day%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fakshata-murty-makes-uk-political-stage-debut-for-best-friend-rishi-sunak-4449806%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BRishi%20And%20I...%26quot%3B%3A%20Akshata%20Murty's%20Viral%20Speech%20At%20UK%20Political%20Stage%20Debut%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENDTV%20is%20now%20available%20on%20WhatsApp%20channels.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whatsapp.com%2Fchannel%2F0029Va4lixw7z4kcvZI9JM12%5C%22%3EClick%20on%20the%20link%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20get%20all%20the%20latest%20updat