hildren%20while%20they%20went%20on%20family%20vacations%2C%20date%20nights%2C%20and%20for%20other%20childcare%20needs%3B%20instead%20they%20were%20unknowingly%20letting%20a%20monster%20walk%20into%20their%20homes%20and%20prey%20upon%20their%20innocent%20children%20in%20the%20vilest%20way.%20I%20am%20incredibly%20proud%20of%20the%20young%20victims%20who%20bravely%20took%20the%20stand%20to%20testify%20against%20their%20abuser%2C%20the%20parents%20who%20were%20by%20their%20side%20every%20step%20of%20the%20way%2C%20and%20the%20parents%20who%20testified%20themselves.%20By%20standing%20up%20to%20this%20predator%20and%20telling%20the%20truth%20about%20what%20he%20did%2C%20they%20are%20ensuring%20that%20the%20voices%20of%20the%20victims%20of%20sexual%20assault%20are%20being%20heard%20while%20they%20are%20protecting%20other%20children%20from%20being%20victimized%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EZakrzewski%20served%20as%20a%20male%20nanny%20for%20families%20across%20Southern%20California%20and%20called%20himself%20%26quot%3Bthe%20original%20Sitter%20Buddy%26quot%3B%20on%20his%20website.%20He%20also%20characterized%20himself%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bmanny%26quot%3B%20who%20provided%20a%20variety%20of%20babysitting%20services%2C%20including%20mentorships%2C%20big%20brother%20relationships%20and%20overnight%20and%20vacation%20babysitting%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Orange%20County%20District%20Attorney's%20Office.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20eighth%20grade%2C%20I%20discovered%20what%20a%20joy%20it%20was%20to%20work%20with%20children%20and%20be%20a%20positive%20impact%20in%20their%20lives%20through%20my%20school's%20'Buddy%20Program%2C'%26quot%3B%20Zakrzewski%20stated%20on%20the%20Sitter%20Buddy%20website.%20%26quot%3BNow%2C%20I%20am%20a%20full-service%20TrustLine%20Certified%20provider%20of%20regular%20and%20on-demand%20childcare%2C%20as%20well%20as%20mentoring%20services%20for%20children.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20committed%20these%20crimes%20between%20January%201%2C%202014%20and%20May%2017%2C%202019.%20He%20faces%20690%20years%20to%20life%20plus%20eight%20years%20when%20he%20is%20sentenced%20on%20November%2017%2C%202023%2C%20at%20the%20Central%20Justice%20Center%20in%20Santa%20Ana%20in%20Department%20C30.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20all%20began%20in%20May%202019%20when%20a%20Laguna%20Beach%20couple%20reported%20to%20the%20police%20that%20their%20babysitter%2C%20Zakrzewski%2C%20had%20touched%20their%20eight-year-old%20son%20inappropriately%20and%20was%20concerned%20for%20the%20safety%20of%20their%20son%20and%20potentially%20other%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20immediately%20opened%20an%20investigation%2C%20which%20led%20to%3Cbr%3E%20the%20identification%20of%20a%20second%20seven-year-old%20victim%20in%20the%20City%20of%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20and%20ten%20more%20boys%20from%20across%20Southern%20California.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696485780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fj9rl6ipg_matthew-zakrzewski_625x300_05_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmale-nanny-sentenced-for-690-years-for-molesting-16-boys-in-us-4451620%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Matthew%20Zakrzewski%20served%20as%20a%20male%20nanny%20for%20families%20across%20Southern%20California%20and%20called%20himself%20%26quot%3Bthe%20original%20Sitter%20Buddy%26quot%3B%20on%20his%20website.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmale-nanny-sentenced-for-690-years-for-molesting-16-boys-in-us-4451620%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmale-nanny-sentenced-for-690-years-for-molesting-16-boys-in-us-4451620%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmale-nanny-sentenced-for-690-years-for-molesting-16-boys-in-us-4451620%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%