ed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EGH%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Look%2C%20it%20is%20possible.%20It%20is%20possible%20for%20a%20few%20reasons.%20I%20mean%2C%20for%20a%20start%2C%20there%20are%2011%20people%20in%20every%20team.%20Effectively%20it%E2%80%99s%201.3%20billion%20versus%2025%20million%20when%20India%20plays%20Australia%20but%20it%E2%80%99s%20still%2011%20on%20the%20field.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20other%20thing%20is%20these%20are%2015-man%20squads%20which%20I%20think%20is%20still%20quite%20weird.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%201975%20there%20were%2014-man%20squads%20and%20yet%20despite%20that%20in%20the%20intervening%20years%20the%20crickets%20became%20all%20about%20match-ups%20and%20shuffling%20around%20for%20a%20change%20of%20conditions%20but%20there%E2%80%99s%20still%20this%20sort%20of%20arbitrary%20restriction%20on%20squads%20that%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%20changed%20unless%20someone%20gets%20injured.%20That%20kind%20of%20leaves%20you%20with%20problems%20if%20three%20or%20four%20of%20your%20leading%20players%20don%E2%80%99t%20get%20into%20form.%20You%20kind%20of%20have%20to%20wait%20for%20them%20to%20get%20back%20into%20form.%20Because%20of%20that%20strange%2C%20arbitrary%20restriction%2C%20it%20does%20kind%20of%20even%20the%20competition%20out%2C%20ever%20so%20slightly.%20I%20think%20it%E2%80%99s%20harder%20in%20India%2C%20the%20pictures%20being%20flatter%2C%20the%20grounds%20tending%20to%20high%20scores.%20It%20will%20be%20a%20game%20that%20is%20decided%20to%20a%20great%20degree%20by%20power%20and%20India%20probably%20has%20the%20most%20powerful%20batting%20lineup%2C%20certainly%20the%20deepest%2C%20the%20most%20agile%2C%20and%20the%20most%20impressive.%20My%20god%2C%20they%20are%20so%20good%2C%20they%E2%80%99re%20wonderful%20to%20watch.%20Whatever%20you%20might%20say%20of%20the%20BCCI%2C%20the%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20is%20absolutely%20fantastic%20to%20watch%20but%20yeah%2C%20there%20is%20just%20the%20outlier%20possibility%20that%20a%20team%20could%20get%20on%20a%20roll%20and%20charge%20through.%20Once%20you%20get%20through%20to%20the%20knockout%20stages%20of%20a%20tournament%2C%20anything%20can%20happen.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ESU%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20That%20sounds%20like%20a%20good%20way%20for%20us%20to%20round%20up%20and%20say%20goodbye%20because%20we%E2%80%99ve%20taken%20a%20lot%20of%20your%20time.%20But%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20just%20thinking%3B%20I%20tend%20to%20be%20a%20lot%20more%20cynical%20than%20you.%20You%E2%80%99re%20saying%20there%20is%20an%20outlier%20possibility%20you%E2%80%99d%20be%20surprised%20at%20how%20many%20people%20inside%20cricket%20are%20saying%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20going%20to%20be%20tough%20for%20the%20Indians%20because%20there%E2%80%99s%20England.%20Just%20before%20we%20go%2C%20what%20do%20you%20make%20of%20this%20England%20resurgence%20as%20an%20Australian%3F%20When%20you%E2%80%99re%20looking%20at%20and%20saying%20what%20is%20this%3F%20Why%20are%20they%20not%20playing%20according%20to%20the%20rule%20book%20that%20is%20more%20than%20120%20years%20old%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EGH%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%20could%20say%20a%20lot%20about%20England%2C%20having%20been%20in%20England%20during%20the%20international%20series.%20I%20did%20come%20back%20with%20some%20pretty%20strong%20impressions%20of%20England%20cricket%E2%80%99s%20self-obsession%2C%20its%20self-absorption.%20They%E2%80%99re%20getting%20high%20on%20their%20own%20supply%20in%20England.%20They%20really%20do%20think%20that%20they%E2%80%99re%20single-handedly%20saving%20cricket%20from%20itself.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20bit%20hard%20to%20take%20but%20they%E2%80%99re%20a%20good%20team%2C%20they%E2%80%99ve%20got%20great%20players%20in%20them.%20They%E2%80%99re%20very%20good%20to%20watch.%20I%20just%20wish%20as%20I%20wrote%20towards%20the%20end%20of%20the%20series%2C%20that%20England%20didn%E2%80%99t%20behave%20like%20they%20expected%20a%20standing%20ovation%20every%20time%20they%20walked%20into%20the%20room.%20Isn%E2%80%99t%20it%20great%20the%20way%20you%20think%20it%20brings%20us%20all%20together%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ESU%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Seriously!%20So%2C%20because%20they%E2%80%99re%20listening%20to%20this.%20I%20mean%20they%20are%20a%20phenomenally%20awesome%20team%20and%20their%20batting%20is%20terrific%20and%20their%20bowling%20is%20terrific.%20Anyhow%20we%E2%80%99ll%20see%20how%20that%20goes%20but%20you%20do%20know%20that%20they%20are%20playing%20them%20in%20Lucknow.%20India%20is%20playing%20England%20in%20Lucknow%20which%20is%20going%20to%20be%20difficult%2C%20the%20Wicket%20has%20been%20relayed.%20It%20got%20very%20bad%20marks%20during%20the%20IPL%20and%20the%20highest%20total%20on%20that%20ground%20is%2C%20I%20think%2C%20140.%20It%20could%20be%20off%20by%20five%20runs%2C%20this%20way%20or%20that%20way.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EGH%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20They%E2%80%99re%20my%20favourite%20games%20though.%20150%20versus%20160%2C%20they%E2%80%99re%20the%20best.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20see%20100%20versus%20300.%20You%20want%20everyone%20to%20count!%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ESU%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20So%2C%20the%20game%20is%20going%20to%20be%20played%20at%20Lucknow%20and%20I%20have%20a%20great%20story%20to%20tell%20you%20about%20Lucknow.%20I%20was%20talking%20to%20one%20of%20my%20friends%2C%20Santosh%2C%20who%20is%20a%20journalist%20there%20and%20he%20was%20telling%20me%20about%20the%20fact%20that%20when%20he%20has%20to%20access%20the%20Lucknow%20Stadium.%20Speak%20about%20user%20friendly%E2%80%A6he%20has%20to%20take%20a%20motorcycle%20up%20to%20a%20point%20and%20then%20slide%20down%20a%20grass%20bank%20that%20is%20a%20shortcut%20to%20the%20stadium.%20Anyhow%2C%20Gideon%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20been%20great%20having%20you.%20We%20could%20talk%20forever.%20Thanks%20very%20much%20and%20hopefully%20we%E2%80%99ll%20have%20a%20great%20World%20Cup%20without%20all%20the%20drama%20and%20not%20too%20much%20of%20the%20ugliness%20that%20we%20are%20all%20fearing.%20Full%20of%20great%20Cricket.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EGH%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20It%20is%20strange%2C%20you%20know%3F%20I%E2%80%99m%20playing%20on%20the%20weekend.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20great%20time%20of%20year%20in%20Australia%2C%20when%20we%E2%80%99re%20just%20about%20to%20go%20into%20the%20cricket%20season.%20For%20a%20club%20cricketer%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20that%20moment%20before%20hope%20collides%20with%20reality.%20So%20I%E2%80%99m%20feeling%20pretty%20optimistic.%20I%20feel%20kind%20of%20optimistic%20about%20this%20World%20Cup.%20I%E2%80%99m%20really%20looking%20forward%20to%20it.%20There%20is%20something%20about%20these%20days%20where%20there%20is%20so%20much%20that%E2%80%99s%20new%2C%20so%20much%20that%E2%80%99s%20instant%20and%20invented%20and%20counterfeit%20and%20made%20up%2C%20that%20something%20that%E2%80%99s%20been%20continuous%20since%201975%20and%20does%20have%20history%20and%20folklore%20and%20great%20moments%20and%20great%20players.%20It%20is%20something%20to%20cherish.%20Yeah%20sure%2C%20let%E2%80%99s%20try%20to%20screen%20out%20everything%20else.%20That%E2%80%99s%20probably%20impossible%2C%20especially%20for%20you%20because%20you%E2%80%99ll%20be%20in%20the%20backdraft%20of%20the%20BJP%20turbojet%20but%20from%20a%20distance%20here%20I%E2%80%99m%20sitting%20in%20for%20some%20really%20good%20cricket.%20Let%E2%80%99s%20hope%20we%20see%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ESU%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Thank%20you%2C%20Gideon.%20Thanks%20so%20much!%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EGH%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20No%20worries%2C%20cheers!%20Okay%2C%20Sharda!%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETranscribed%20by%20Karizma%20Ahmed.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696484703000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F05110819%2FF7cIVujasAAu0e5.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fcricket-world-cup-sharda-ugra-gideon-haigh-transcript%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'The%20ICC%20does%20require%20the%20governance%20of%20cricket%20in%20countries%20to%20be%20free%20of%20government%20interference.%20It%20is%20something%20that%20we%20talk%20about%20all%20the%20time%20in%20the%20context%20of%20other%20countries...but%20never%20India...You're%20not%20even%20allowed%20to%20mention%20it%2C'%20says%20Gideon%20Haigh.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fcricket-world-cup-sharda-ugra-gideon-haigh-transcript%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rishi%20Sunak%20Wants%20To%20Raise%20Legal%20Age%20To%20Buy%20Cigarettes%20Every%20Year%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUK%20Prime%20Minister%20Rishi%20Sunak%20aims%20to%20gradually%20raise%20the%20legal%20age%20for%20consuming%20cigarettes%20in%20a%20move%20that%20would%20introduce%20a%20ban%20for%20the%20next%20generation.%20The%20age%20would%20increase%20by%20one%20year%20annually%20so%20that%20%26quot%3Ba%2014-year-old%20today%20would%20never%20legally%20be%20sold%20a%20cigarette%2C%26quot%3B%20Sunak%20said%20at%20the%20Conservative%20Party%20conference%20in%20Manchester%20on%20Wednesday.%20The%20government%20also%20plans%20to%20restrict%20the%20availability%20of%20disposable%20vapes%20and%20will%20look%20at%20the%20packaging%20and%20flavors%20of%20those%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20proposal%20would%20have%20to%20be%20approved%20by%20the%20UK%20parliament%2C%20with%20Sunak%20saying%20it%20will%20be%20a%20free%20vote%2C%20asking%20politicians%20to%20make%20their%20decision%20as%20%26quot%3Ba%20matter%20of%20conscience.%26quot%3B%20Sunak%20added%20that%20smoking%20puts%20pressure%20on%20the%20NHS%2C%20with%20costs%20of%20%C2%A317%20billion%20(%2420.7%20billion)%20a%20year%2C%20and%20the%20move%20would%20help%20the%20UK%20toward%20its%20goal%20to%20become%20smoke-free%20by%202030.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShares%20of%20Imperial%20Brands%20Plc%2C%20the%20biggest%20seller%20of%20cigarettes%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20fell%20as%20much%20as%204.3%25%20in%20London.%20British%20American%20Tobacco%20Plc%2C%20which%20gets%20most%20of%20its%20sales%20from%20markets%20outside%20Britain%2C%20was%20down%201.9%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20measure%20would%20be%20one%20of%20the%20most%20aggressive%20anti-smoking%20policies%20in%20the%20world%2C%20though%20the%20UK%20wouldn't%20be%20the%20first.%20New%20Zealand%20last%20year%20passed%20a%20law%20prohibiting%20the%20sale%20of%20cigarettes%20to%20anyone%20born%20after%202008.%20The%20current%20legal%20age%20to%20buy%20cigarettes%20in%20the%20UK%20is%2018.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETobacco%20companies%20are%20racing%20to%20offer%20alternatives%2C%20such%20as%20vapes%2C%20devices%20that%20heat%20tobacco%20and%20oral%20nicotine.%20Sunak%20said%20the%20UK%20must%20%26quot%3Bact%20before%20vaping%20becomes%20endemic%2C%26quot%3B%20given%20that%20one%20in%20five%20children%20have%20used%20the%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20proposal%20to%20ban%20the%20legal%20sale%20of%20cigarettes%20over%20time%20threatens%20significant%20unintended%20consequences%2C%26quot%3B%20Imperial%20Brands%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20Bloomberg.%20%26quot%3BOn%20vaping%2C%20we%20will%20continue%20to%20engage%20with%20the%20government%20to%20create%20effective%20policies%20which%20prevent%20youth%20access.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBritish%20American%20Tobacco%20said%20it%20supports%20%26quot%3Bthe%20government's%20ambition%20to%20further%20reduce%20smoking%20rates%2C%26quot%3B%20while%20noting%20the%20move%20would%20add%20a%20burden%20on%20the%20police%20to%20enforce%20more%20tobacco%20control%20policies.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESmoke-Free%20Generation%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20plans%20are%20negative%20for%20Imperial%20Brands%20and%20Japan%20Tobacco%20Inc.%20because%20of%20its%20large%20exposure%20to%20UK%20combustibles%2C%20while%20a%20%26quot%3Bclear%20positive%26quot%3B%20for%20British%20American%20Tobacco%20given%20the%20company's%20minimal%20presence%20in%20that%20segment%20and%20leadership%20in%20non-disposable%20vapes%2C%20Jefferies%20analyst%20Owen%20Bennett%20said%20in%20a%20note.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20proportion%20of%2018-%20to%2024-year-olds%20who%20smoke%20rose%20to%20one%20in%20three%20from%20one%20in%20four%20during%20the%20Covid%20pandemic%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20commissioned%20for%20the%20government%20last%20year.%20The%20report%20also%20said%20smokers%20in%20the%20most%20economically%20deprived%20parts%20of%20the%20UK%20devote%20a%20disproportionate%20amount%20of%20their%20income%20to%20tobacco%2C%20with%20the%20average%20smoker%20in%20northeast%20England%20spending%20more%20than%2010%25%20of%20their%20income%20on%20smoking.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRaising%20the%20age%20of%20sale%20on%20tobacco%20products%20is%20a%20critical%20step%20on%20the%20road%20to%20creating%20the%20first%20ever%20smokefree%20generation%2C%26quot%3B%20Michelle%20Mitchell%2C%20Cancer%20Research%20UK's%20chief%20executive%20officer%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20released%20by%20the%20Science%20Media%20Centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696484700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F817ag8s_rishi-sunak-bloomberg_625x300_05_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Frishi-sunak-wants-to-raise-legal-age-to-buy-cigarettes-every-year-4451572%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rishi%20Sunak%20aims%20to%20gradually%20raise%20the%20legal%20age%20for%20consuming%20cigarettes%20in%20a%20move%20that%2