pital%20who%20has%20been%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20highlighting%20the%20failures%20of%20state%20establishments%20over%20the%20last%2040%20years.%20Over%20the%20last%2010%20years%2C%20he%20had%20been%20particularly%20critical%20of%20the%20alleged%20authoritarian%20policies%20and%20measures%20of%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CParanjoy%2C%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20one%20of%20my%20colleagues%20informed%2C%20even%20as%20most%20of%20us%20were%20slowly%20waking%20up%20to%20the%20scale%20of%20the%20raids.%20Paranjoy%20Guha%20Thakurta%2C%20in%20the%20last%2040%20years%2C%20has%20consistently%20exposed%20crony%20practices%20of%20Indian%20governments.%20Most%20recently%2C%20he%20worked%20on%20a%20series%20of%20stories%20about%20the%20Adani%20group%E2%80%99s%20alleged%20financial%20frauds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBy%209%20am%2C%20it%20was%20clear%20that%20the%20police%20were%20searching%20the%20homes%20of%20journalists%20who%20were%20related%20in%20some%20fashion%20with%20Newsclick%2C%20a%20portal%20which%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20taking%20funds%20from%20a%20pro-China%20lobbyist%20in%20the%20US%2C%20Neville%20Roy%20Singham.%20But%20then%2C%20we%20soon%20learnt%20that%20police%20had%20registered%20a%20fresh%20case%20against%20under%20the%20Unlawful%20Activities%20(Prevention)%20Act%2C%20a%20stringent%20law%20that%20should%20be%20sparingly%20used%20against%20terrorists.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fmedia-organisations-write-chandrachud-freedom-press%5C%22%3E18%20Media%20Organisations%20Write%20to%20CJI%20Chandrachud%20Expressing%20Alarm%20Over%20Attacks%20on%20Press%20Freedom%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20prominent%20journalists%20who%20came%20under%20the%20scanner%20were%20Bhasha%20Singh%2C%20a%20lifelong%20anti-caste%20activist%20who%20has%20been%20exposing%20the%20prevalence%20of%20manual%20scavenging%20practices%20in%C2%A0%3Cspan%3EIndia%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20Subodh%20Verma%2C%20a%20former%C2%A0%3Cem%3ETimes%20of%C2%A0%3Cspan%3EIndia%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0editor%20whose%20work%20on%20data%20analysis%20is%20peerless%2C%C2%A0%3Cem%3ENewsClick%E2%80%99s%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0founding%20editor%20Prabir%20Purkayastha%2C%20a%20scholar%2C%20scientist%20and%20columnist%2C%20and%20critical%20television%20anchors%20like%20Abhisar%20Sharma%20and%20Urmilesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMost%20men%20whose%20homes%20were%20searched%20were%20taken%20away%20to%20the%20Lodhi%20Colony%E2%80%99s%20special%20cell%20police%20station%20where%20they%20were%20questioned%20for%20over%2010%20hours.%20As%20some%20of%20us%20descended%20to%20the%20Lodhi%20colony%20police%20station%2C%20we%20were%20told%20that%20none%20could%20enter%20the%20premises.%20%E2%80%9CEven%20lawyers%20are%20not%20being%20allowed%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20lower%20level%20police%20official%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F05100450%2Fsignal-2023-10-03-154153_002-1.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F05100450%2Fsignal-2023-10-03-154153_002-1.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F05100450%2Fsignal-2023-10-03-154153_002-1-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F05100450%2Fsignal-2023-10-03-154153_002-1-1024x768.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-678353%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EScene%20at%20the%20Special%20Cell%20HQ%20of%20Delhi%20Police%20in%20Lodhi%20Colony%20on%20October%203.%20Photo%3A%20The%20Wire%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EWe%20waited%20for%20the%20detained%20journalists%20to%20be%20released%20and%20give%20their%20statements%2C%20unsure%20of%20whether%20they%20have%20been%20formally%20arrested%20or%20detained%20only%20for%20questioning.%20As%20daylight%20faded%2C%20many%20of%20those%20began%20to%20come%20out%20but%20darkness%20still%20prevailed%20over%20the%20charges%20under%20which%20they%20were%20detained.%20By%20late%20evening%2C%20the%20police%20gave%20a%20statement%20that%20Prabir%20Purkayastha%2C%20founding%20editor%20of%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0and%20the%20organisation%E2%80%99s%20HR%20head%20Amit%20Chakravarty%2C%20had%20been%20arrested%20under%20UAPA%20sections.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlmost%20all%20of%20them%20said%20upon%20their%20release%20that%20the%20police%20kept%20asking%20them%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fnewsclick-raids-journos-questioned-delhi-riots-farmers-protest-covid-crisis%5C%22%3Ewhether%20they%20covered%20stories%20on%20the%20anti-Muslim%20Delhi%20riots%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20year-long%20farmers%20agitation%2C%20the%20anti-CAA%20protests%2C%20and%20even%20the%20COVID-19%20crisis.%20They%20were%20asked%20why%20they%20covered%20these%20stories%20that%20portrayed%20%3Cspan%3EIndia%3C%2Fspan%3E%C2%A0in%20a%20poor%20light.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAre%20we%20to%20assume%20that%20the%20journalists%20should%20now%20skip%20the%20most%20important%20stories%20of%20the%20time%20because%20they%20may%20embarrass%20the%20government%20of%20the%20day%3F%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fcovid-19-journalists-arrested-booked-report%5C%22%3EOver%2050%20journalists%20working%20in%C2%A0%3Cspan%3EIndia%3C%2Fspan%3E%E2%80%99s%20hinterland%20have%20been%20booked%20earlier%3C%2Fa%3E%20under%20different%20charges%20for%20covering%20the%20conditions%20in%20which%20the%20poor%20had%20to%20live%20in%20during%20the%20COVID-19%20lockdown.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fsummoned-raided-censored-crackdown-on-journalists-is-the-new-normal-in-kashmir%5C%22%3EMany%20Kashmiri%20journalists%20have%20also%20been%20targeted%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20security%20agencies%2C%20forcing%20their%20news%20platforms%20to%20shut%20down.%20But%20October%203%2C%202023%20will%20be%20etched%20in%20our%20memory%20as%20the%20day%20when%20simultaneous%20raids%20were%20conducted%20on%20nearly%2050%20journalists%2C%20many%20of%20whom%20are%20prominent%20figures.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWe%20still%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20the%20specific%20charges%20slapped%20against%20the%20news%20portal%2C%20but%20some%20television%20channels%2C%20known%20for%20pro-government%20coverage%2C%20claimed%20that%20the%20portal%20had%20routed%20some%20of%20the%20Chinese%20funds%20to%20human%20rights%20activists%20Gautam%20Navlakha%20and%20Teesta%20Setalvad%2C%20who%20are%20already%20under%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20scanner.%20The%20police%20claimed%20that%20Purakayastha%20and%20Chakravarty%20have%20been%20accused%20of%20taking%20Rs%2038%20crore%20from%20Chinese%20entities%2C%20a%20portion%20of%20which%20was%20routed%20towards%20the%20accounts%20of%20Gautam%20Navlakha%20and%20Teesta%20Setalvad%2C%20both%20prominent%20human%20rights%20activists%20and%20vocal%20critics%20of%20the%20Modi%20government%20who%20already%20face%20serious%20criminal%20charges.%20Navlakha%20is%20under%20house%20arrest%2C%20while%20Setalvad%20secured%20bail%20after%20being%20imprisoned%20for%20days%20in%20a%20case%20of%20financial%20fraud.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EYet%2C%20none%20of%20the%20drastic%20actions%20taken%20by%20the%20police%20made%20much%20sense.%20Homes%20of%20junior%20staffers%2C%20freelancers%20who%20may%20have%20contributed%20an%20article%20or%20two%20to%C2%A0%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20consultants%2C%20even%20graphic%20designers%20and%20cartoonists%2C%20political%20activists%2C%20a%20stand-up%20comedian%20and%20academics%20who%20have%20appeared%20in%20the%20website%E2%80%99s%20programmes%2C%20were%20also%20under%20the%20scanner.%20Their%20homes%20were%20almost%20invaded.%20Their%20phones%2C%20laptops%2C%20hard%20disks%2C%20and%20even%20books%20were%20seized.%20A%20majority%20of%20them%20didn%E2%80%99t%20get%20any%20mandatory%20seizure%20memo%20and%20hash%20value%20of%20gadgets%20being%20taken%20away%20by%20the%20police.%20Many%20who%20were%20raided%20also%20complained%20that%20the%20police%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20a%20search%20warrant.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20case%20of%20financial%20fraud%20against%C2%A0%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%20was%20already%20being%20pursued.%20Last%20week%2C%20the%20Delhi%20high%20court%20ruled%20that%20no%20coercive%20action%20could%20be%20taken%20against%20Purkayastha%20or%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0until%20the%20next%20hearing%2C%20scheduled%20next%20week.%20However%2C%20a%20fresh%20case%20under%20the%20draconian%20provisions%20of%20UAPA%20case%20has%20now%20allowed%20the%20police%20to%20not%20only%20conduct%20fresh%20raids%20on%C2%A0%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0journalists%20but%20also%20seal%20the%20organisation%E2%80%99s%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMost%20scribes%20believe%20that%20these%20unprecedented%20raids%20were%20conducted%20to%20create%20a%20chilling%20effect%20on%20journalists%2C%20to%20silence%20them%20ahead%20of%20the%202024%20general%20elections.%20The%20searches%20provoked%20a%20spontaneous%20protest%20meeting%20at%20the%20Press%20Club%20of%C2%A0%3Cspan%3EIndia%3C%2Fspan%3E.%20Many%20journalist%20groups%20have%20also%20planned%20a%20protest%20march%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20Delhi%20today.%20Many%20will%20also%20write%20appeals%20to%20the%20President%20of%C2%A0%3Cspan%3EIndia%3C%2Fspan%3E%C2%A0and%20other%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%3C%2Fspan%3E%C2%A0is%20placed%20at%20an%20abysmal%20161%20among%20the%20180%20countries%20surveyed%20in%20the%20Press%20Freedom%20Index%20and%20has%20fallen%2050%20points%20over%20the%20last%2010%20years.%20The%20criminalisation%20of%20dissent%20has%20become%20the%20new%20normal%20in%20present%20day%C2%A0%3Cspan%3EIndia%3C%2Fspan