2https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F651d2442617692f0d03e898e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222623%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20still%20from%20Mei%20Liao's%20%23tinnedfishtok%20videos%3Cp%3EMei%20Liao%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20creators%20behind%20the%20trend%2C%20TikTok's%20canned%20seafood%20renaissance%20is%20happening%20because%20of%20how%20easily%20tinned%20fish%20fits%20in%20with%20tightening%20budgets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20believe%20the%20current%20state%20of%20the%20US%20economy%20is%20helping%20to%20fuel%20the%20popularity%20of%20tinned%20fish%20too%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40robhomecook%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERobert%20McGinnis%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20reviews%20tinned%20fish%20on%20his%20TikTok%20channel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20the%20price%20of%20everything%20continues%20to%20rise%2C%20it's%20become%20harder%20to%20make%20an%20affordable%2C%20nutritious%2C%20and%20filling%20meal%20while%20staying%20within%20budgets%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Insider.%20McGinnis%20also%20pointed%20to%20tinned%20fish%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0which%20often%20comes%20in%20at%20under%20%243%20%E2%80%94%20as%20a%20low-cost%2C%20shelf%20stable%2C%20and%20versatile%20product%20that%20can%20be%20used%20as%20a%20snack%20or%20as%20an%20ingredient%20in%20a%20larger%20meal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFrankly%20it%20doesn't%20get%20much%20easier%20than%20just%20peeling%20open%20a%20can%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40daywithmei%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMei%20Liao%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20TikTok%20creator%20whose%20educational%20videos%20on%20tinned%20fish%20regularly%20rack%20up%20over%20100%2C000%20views%2C%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20working%2040%20hours%20a%20week%20and%20then%20I'm%20going%20to%20school%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%20%26quot%3BSo%20I%20found%20it%20was%20a%20great%20alternative%20to%20cooking%20%E2%80%94%20and%20part%20of%20it%20is%20also%20the%20cost%20and%20convenience.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20fanfare%20over%20tinned%20fish%20isn't%20contained%20to%20TikTok.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdam%20Bent%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20Vancouver-based%20seafood%20cannery%20Scout%2C%20told%20Insider%20the%20company%20had%20seen%20a%20144%25%20increase%20in%20sales%20since%20the%20viral%20tinned%20fish%20date%20night%20video%20by%20TikToker%20Ali%20Hooke%20in%20September%20last%20year.%20Insider%20could%20not%20independently%20verify%20the%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECanned%20fish%20has%20been%20a%20staple%20of%20some%20Asian%20and%20European%20cultures.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20collage%20of%20tinned%20fish%20dishes%20prepared%20by%20Molly%20Moss%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F651cf71a2ce014759e743a8c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20collage%20of%20tinned%20fish%20dishes%20prepared%20by%20Molly%20Moss%3Cp%3EMolly%20Moss%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20popularity%20of%20tinned%20fish%20isn't%20just%20about%20food%20on%20a%20budget.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20people%20think%20that%20if%20you%20can%20get%20a%20can%20of%20sardines%20for%2099%20cents%2C%20then%20all%20tinned%20fish%20should%20be%20super%20cheap.%20But%20that's%20not%20the%20case%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40moss_en_place%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMolly%20Moss%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20another%20TikTok%20creator.%20Moss%20said%20she%20got%20her%20start%20on%20Instagram%2C%20gaining%2030%2C000%20followers%20over%20two%20months%20with%20her%20videos%20about%20tinned%20fish.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMoss%20said%20there%20were%20premium%20and%20luxury%20tins%20that%20could%20go%20up%20to%20%2450%20%E2%80%94%20but%20found%20tins%20costing%20around%20%2410%20to%20%2415%20to%20be%20her%20sweet%20spot%20for%20value%20and%20quality.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20TikTok%20creators%20who%20spoke%20to%20Insider%20said%20while%20they%20loved%20seeing%20tinned%20fish's%20rise%20in%20popularity%2C%20they%20think%20the%20people%20who%20see%20it%20purely%20as%20a%20TikTok%20trend%20are%20being%20unfairly%20dismissive%20of%20the%20dish.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20though%20novel%20to%20Americans%2C%20canned%20fish%20has%20long%20been%20a%20part%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fsites%2Felizabethkarmel%2F2023%2F09%2F18%2Ftrending-tinned-fish-is-something-old-that-is-new-again%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPortuguese%20and%20Spanish%20food%20culture%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20Chinese%20American%2C%20Liao%20explained%20that%20her%20upbringing%20involved%20plenty%20of%20canned%20foods%20%E2%80%94%20like%20luncheon%20meat%20and%20canned%20dace%20with%20black%20beans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20so%2C%20tinned%20fish%20can%20be%20seen%20as%20%26quot%3Bsomething%20that%20is%20cheap%2C%20oftentimes%20perceived%20as%20being%20inferior%20to%20fresh%20food%2C%26quot%3B%20Liao%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20Liao%20isn't%20alone%20in%20thinking%20that%20canned%20foods%20have%20a%20bad%20rep%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTinned%20fish%20has%20been%20under-appreciated%20in%20the%20US%20market%20for%20a%20long%20time%20and%20all%20of%20a%20sudden%20people%20are%20shining%20a%20light%20on%20how%20delicious%20it%20can%20be%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Moss.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20while%20it%20feels%20'new%2C'%20there%20is%20already%20a%20huge%20selection%20of%20options%20readily%20available%20from%20all%20over%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20McGinnis%20said%20that%20he%20loves%20how%20the%20tinned%20fish%20renaissance%20on%20TikTok%20is%20breaking%20down%20our%20stigma%20towards%20certain%20foods.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBringing%20strong%20and%20'unusual'%20foods%20to%20the%20forefront%20makes%20them%20more%20accepted%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-tinned-fish-trend-obsession-affordable-luxury-can-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696477388000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F651cf3262ce014759e7439d6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-tinned-fish-trend-obsession-affordable-luxury-can-2023-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Creators%20told%20Insider%20that%20while%20they%20appreciate%20the%20item's%20newfound%20popularity%2C%20they%20feel%20tinned%20fish%20is%20unjustly%20dismissed%20as%20merely%20a%20TikTok%20trend.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kteo%40insider.com%20(Kai%20Xiang%20Teo)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-tinned-fish-trend-obsession-affordable-luxury-can-2023-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Did%20Nepal%20Earthquake%20Trigger%20The%20Cloud%20Burst%20In%20Sikkim%3F%20Experts%20To%20Study%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EScientists%20are%20exploring%20whether%20the%20strong%20earthquake%20that%20struck%20Nepal%20and%20the%20surrounding%20region%20on%20Tuesday%20is%20responsible%20for%20the%20south%20Lhonak%20lake%20outburst%2C%20which%20triggered%20a%20flash%20flood%20in%20the%20Teesta%20river%20basin%20in%20Sikkim.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20lake%20outburst%20also%20resulted%20in%20the%20breach%20of%20the%20Chungthang%20dam%2C%20which%20is%20the%20largest%20hydropower%20project%20in%20the%20state.%20This%20dam%20is%20part%20of%20the%201%2C200-megawatt%20(MW)%20Teesta%20Stage%20III%20Hydro%20Electric%20Project%2C%20in%20which%20the%20state%20government%20is%20the%20majority%20stakeholder.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESatellite%20images%20released%20by%20the%20Hyderabad-based%20National%20Remote%20Sensing%20Centre%20showed%20that%20the%20area%20of%20south%20Lhonak%20lake%20reduced%20by%20over%20100%20hectares%20compared%20to%20its%20size%20on%20September%2017.%20This%20suggests%20that%20the%20lake%20outburst%20caused%20a%20flash%20flood%20in%20the%20Teesta%20River%20basin%20in%20north%20Sikkim.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOfficials%20said%20at%20least%20eight%20people%20died%20and%2069%20more%2C%20including%2022%20army%20personnel%2C%20were%20missing.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EScientists%20are%20exploring%20whether%20the%20earthquake%20that%20hit%20Nepal%20might%20be%20a%20cause%20of%20the%20flash%20floods%20in%20Sikkim.%20The%20lake%20was%20already%20vulnerable%20and%20covered%20an%20area%20of%20168%20hectares.%20Its%20area%20has%20now%20reduced%20to%2060%20hectares%2C%20indicating%20that%20about%20100%20hectares%20of%20water%20volume%20has%20breached%20the%20level%2C%20explained%20a%20senior%20official%20at%20the%20Central%20Water%20Commission%20(CWC)%20to%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20official%20stated%20that%20while%20it's%20difficult%20to%20determine%20right%20now%2C%20a%20cloud%20burst%20does%20not%20cause%20such%20results.%20Some%20experts%20who%20have%20visited%20the%20site%20believe%20that%20the%20earthquake%20may%20have%20triggered%20the%20floods%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20flood%20alerts%20were%20also%20shared%20with%20Bangladesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20NRSC%20satellite%20imagery%20revealed%20that%20the%20lake%20covered%20approximately%20162.7%20hectares.%20Its%20area%20increased%20to%20167.4%20hectares%20on%20September%2028%20but%20drastically%20reduced%20to%2060.3%20hectares.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20satellite%20data%2C%20it%20is%20evident%20that%20the%20lake%20area%20has%20significantly%20reduced%20compared%20to%20the%20September%2017%2C%202023%2C%20RISAT%201A%20MRS%20satellite%20data%2C%20read%20an%20NRSC%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20glacial%20lake%20outburst%20flood%20(GLOF)%20in%20portions%20of%20Lhonak%20Lake%2C%20Mangan%20district%2C%20which%20caused%20a%20rapid%20rise%20in%20water%20levels%20with%20very%20high%20velocities%20downstream%20along%20the%20Teesta%20River%20Basin%20in%20the%20early%20hours%20of%20October%204%2C%20has%20resulted%20in%20severe%20damage%20in%20Mangan%2C%20Gangtok%2C%20Pakyong%2C%20and%20Namchi%20districts%2C%20the%20State%20Disaster%20Management%20Authority%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Chungthang%20NHPC%20dam%20and%20the%20bridge%20were%20washed%20away.%20Two%20bridges%20at%20Minshithang%2C%20one%20bridge%20at%20Zema%2C%20and%20Ritchu%20Bridge%2C%20including%20the%20Sangkhalang%20bridge%2C%20were%20washed%20away%2C%20the%20state%20government%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20SDMA's%20statement%20highlighted%20that%20following%20the%20lake%20outburst%2C%20the%20water%20level%20in%20the%20rivers%20rose%20at%20a%20speed%20of%2015%20meters%20per%20second.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20lake%20outburst%20caused%20extensive%20damage%20to%20life%20and%20property%2C%20including%20the%20breakdown%20of%20road%20networks%20and%20communication.%20Several%20vital%20bridges%20connecting%20to%20the%20forward%20border%20areas%20with%20Sikkim%20have%20been%20washed%20away%20due%20to%20the%20flash%20floods%20in%20Mangan%2C%20Gangtok%2C%20Pakyong%2C%20and%20Namchi%20districts%20of%20Sikkim%2C%20according%20to%20Sikkim's%20Chief%20Secretary%20Vijay%20Bhushan%20Pathak.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EArun%20B%20Shrestha%2C%20senior%20climate%20change%20specialist%2C%20the%20International%20Centre%20for%20Integrated%20Mountain%20Development%20(ICIMOD)%2C%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BWe're%20facing%20a%20devastating%20flash%20flood%20in%20the%20Teesta%20River.%20Information%20is%20fragmented%2C%20but%20it%20appears%20heavy%20rainfall%20from%20a%20Bay%20of%20Bengal%20low-pressure%20depression%20triggered%20the%20disaster.%20This%20seems%20like%20another%20unfortunate%20example%20of%20cascading%20hazards.%26quot%3B%20He%20said%20that%20the%20institute%20recorded%20exceedingly%20high%20precipitation%2C%20exceeding%20100%20mm%20within%20the%20last%2024%20hours%20in%20the%20vicinity%20.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMiriam%20Jackson%2C%20senior%20cryosphere%20specialist%2C%20ICIMOD%2C%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BIntense%20rain%20has%20led%20to%20this%20catastrophic%20situation%20in%20Sikkim%20where%20the%20rain%20has%20triggered%20a%20glacial%20lake%20outburst%20flood%20and%20damaged%20a%20dam%20and%20caused%20loss%20of%20life%20and%20caused%20further%20damage%20to%20roads%20and%20infrastructure.%20We%20observe%20that%20such%20extreme%20events%20increase%20in%20frequency%20as%20the%20climate%20continues%20to%20warm%20and%20takes%20us%20into%20unknown%20territory.%26quot%3B%20Sikkim%20has%20733%20glacial%20lakes%2C%20with%20288%20located%20above%20an%20altitude%20of%205%2C000%20m%2C%20according%20to%20NRSC.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20South%20Asia%20Network%20of%20Dams%2C%20Rivers%20and%20People%2C%20south%20Lhonak%20lake%20is%20a%20glacial-moraine-dammed%20lake%2C%20located%20in%20Sikkim's%20far%20northwestern%20region.%20It%20is%20one%20of%20the%20fastest%20expanding%20lakes%20in%20the%20Sikkim%20Himalaya%20region%2C%20and%20one%20of%20the%2014%20potentially%20dangerous%20lakes%20susceptible%20to%20GLOF.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20lake%20is%20located%20at%205%2C200%20m%20(17%2C100%20ft)%20above%20sea%20level.%20It%20formed%20due%20to%20the%20melting%20of%20the%20Lhonak%20glacier.%20The%20lake%20is%20rapidly%20growing%20in%20size%20in%20an%20abnormally%20rapid%20manner%20due%20to%20the%20melting%20of%20the%20lake's%20associated%20South%20Lhonak%20glacier%20and%20additional%20melt%20water%20from%20the%20adjacent%20North%20Lhonak%20and%20main%20Lhonak%20glaciers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20study%20published%20in%20the%20journal%20Science%20Direct%20in%202021%20stated%20that%20since%20these%20lakes%20are%20mainly%20situated%20in%20remote%20and%20unsettled%20mountain%20valleys%2C%20GLOFs%20could%20claim%20lives%20and%20damage%20assets%20tens%20of%20kilometers%20downstream.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGLOFs%20occur%20when%20lakes%20formed%20by%20melting%20glaciers%20suddenly%20burst%20open.%20This%20can%20happen%20due%20to%20various%20reasons%2C%20such%20as%20too%20much%20water%20accumulating%20in%20the%20lake%20or%20triggers%20like%20earthquakes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20lake%20bursts%2C%20it%20releases%20a%20massive%20amount%20of%20water%20all%20at%20once%2C%20causing%20flash%20floods%20downstream.%20These%20floods%20can%20be%20very%20destructive%20and%20dangerous%20to%20people%20and%20the%20environment%20in%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EInfrastructure%20exposed%20to%20GLOFs%20in%20the%20Teesta%20valley%20suggests%20that%20many%20settlements%20and%20assets%20along%20the%20river%20channel%20at%20Chungthang%20are%20potentially%20exposed%20to%20future%20GLOFs.%20This%20indicates%20the%20need%20for%20a%20comprehensive%20environmental%20impact%20assessment%20and%20potential%20GLOF%20risk%20mitigation%20measures.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20largest%20GLOF%20events%20have%20occurred%20in%20the%20Himalayas%2C%20such%20as%20the%202013%20Chorabari%20lake%20outburst%2C%20known%20as%20the%20Kedarnath%20disaster%20in%20Uttarakhand.%20The%20swelling%20of%20the%20Jhelum%20river%20led%20to%20Kashmir%20floods%20in%202014%2C%20and%20Parechu%20river%20flash%20floods%20occurred%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20in%202005.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Kedarnath%20disaster%2C%20caused%20by%20a%20multi-day%20cloudburst%20between%20June%2016-17%2C%202013%2C%20became%20India's%20worst%20natural%20disaster%20since%20the%202004%20Indian%20Ocean%20Tsunami.%20The%20combination%20of%20melting%20from%20the%20Chorabari%20glacier%20and%20the%20eruption%20of%20the%20Mandakini%20river%20blocked%20the%20rivers%2C%20causing%20major%20overflow.%20More%20than%205%2C700%20people%20were%20presumed%20dead.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDestruction%20of%20bridges%20and%20roads%20trapped%20around%20300%2C000%20pilgrims%20and%20tourists%20in%20the%20valleys%20leading%20to%20three%20of%20the%20four%20Hindu%20Chota%20Char%20Dham%20pilgrimage%20sites.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20flash%20flood%20in%20Uttarakhand's%20Chamoli%20district%20on%207%20February%202021%20ravaged%20through%20the%20valleys%20of%20the%20Rishi%20Ganga%2C%20Dhauliganga%20and%20Alaknanda%20rivers%2C%20swept%20away%20the%20unfinished%20Tapovan%20Vishnugad%20Hydropower%20Project%20and%20inflicted%20substantial%20damage%20on%20the%20Rishi%20Ganga%20Hydropower%20Project.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20study%20published%20in%20the%20journal%20Nature%20earlier%20this%20year%20stated%20that%2015%20million%20people%20worldwide%20are%20exposed%20to%20potential%20GLOF%20impacts.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPopulations%20in%20High%20Mountains%20Asia%20(HMA)%20are%20the%20most%20exposed%2C%20living%20closest%20to%20glacial%20lakes%2C%20with%20one%20million%20people%20living%20within%2010%20km%20of%20a%20glacial%20lake.%20More%20than%20half%20of%20the%20globally%20exposed%20population%20is%20found%20in%20just%20four%20countries%3A%20India%2C%20Pakistan%2C%20Peru%2C%20and%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696477020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F80lg4ba_sikkim-flood-650_625x300_04_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdid-nepal-earthquake-trigger-the-cloud-burst-in-sikkim-experts-to-study-4450515%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Scientists%20are%20exploring%20whether%20the%20strong%20earthquake%20that%20struck%20Nepal%20and%20the%20surrounding%20region%20on%20Tuesday%20is%20responsible%20for%20the%20south%20Lhonak%20lake%20outburst%2C%20which%20triggered%20a%20flash%20flood%20in%20the%20Teesta%20river%20basin%20in%20Sikkim.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.co