er%20at%20FTX%20I%20may%20have%20unwittingly%20written%20code%20that%20contributed%20to%20the%20commission%20of%20a%20crime%2C%26quot%3B%20Yedidia%20said%20on%20the%20witness%20stand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProsecutors%20allege%20that%20Sam%20Bankman-Fried%20defrauded%20depositors%20and%20investors%20at%20FTX%2C%20the%20cryptocurrency%20exchange%20he%20once%20ran%2C%20in%20part%20by%20commingling%20customer%20funds%20with%20Alameda%20Research%2C%20a%20crypto%20hedge%20fund%20he%20also%20controlled.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225760%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Adam%20Yedidia%20Sam%20bankman%20fried%20trial%20court%20illustration%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F651dda9f42ecf94db4784ff6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223455%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThis%20courtroom%20sketch%20shows%20Adam%20Yedidia%2C%20former%20FTX%20and%20Alameda%20Research%20employee%20and%20former%20friend%20of%20Sam%20Bankman-Fried%2C%20testifying%2C%20Wednesday%2C%20Oct.%204%2C%202023.%20%3Cp%3EAP%20Photo%2FElizabeth%20Williams%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20Yedidia%20finished%20his%20testimony%20on%20Wednesday%20afternoon%20%E2%80%94%20to%20be%20continued%20on%20Thursday%20morning%20%E2%80%94%20he%20didn't%20talk%20about%20the%20software%20code%20he%20was%20worried%20about.%20But%20prosecutors%20say%20that%20Bankman-Fried%20directed%20employees%20to%20write%20computer%20code%20that%20would%20allow%20funds%20to%20move%20seamlessly%20between%20FTX%20and%20Alameda%20Research%2C%20allowing%20the%20firm%20to%20take%20FTX%20customer%20funds%20and%20use%20the%20money%20for%20risky%20cryptocurrency%20bets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYedidia%20shifted%20in%20his%20seat%20between%20questions%2C%20which%20he%20answered%20quickly%20and%20concisely.%20US%20District%20Judge%20Lewis%20Kaplan%2C%20who's%20overseeing%20the%20case%2C%20granted%20him%20immunity%20ahead%20of%20the%20trial's%20start%20earlier%20this%20week.%20Prosecutors%20asked%20for%20immunity%20for%20two%20witnesses%20in%20the%20case%2C%20according%20to%20letters%20filed%20to%20the%20court%20docket.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProsecutors%20separately%20reached%20cooperation%20agreements%20with%20three%20executives%20in%20Bankman-Fried's%20orbit%2C%20including%20Alameda%20Research%20CEO%20Caroline%20Ellison%20and%20FTX%20cofounder%20Gary%20Wang.%20Prosecutors%20said%20Wang%20would%20testify%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Yedidia%20can't%20be%20prosecuted%20for%20what%20he'll%20testify%20about%2C%20he%20said%20he%20understood%20he%20could%20still%20face%20criminal%20charges%20for%20perjury%20if%20he%20lies%20on%20the%20stand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYedidia%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bclose%20friend%26quot%3B%20of%20Bankman-Fried%20for%20years%20before%20he%20ended%20up%20at%20FTX%2C%20he%20testified.%20The%20two%20were%20%26quot%3Bclose%26quot%3B%20at%20MIT%2C%20and%20met%20at%20a%20group%20house%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcurrencies%2Fsam-bankman-fried-profile-details-college-years-cryptocurrency-billionaire-ftx-2021-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehe%20once%20described%20as%3C%2Fa%3E%20akin%20to%20a%20frat%20house%2C%20%26quot%3Bbut%20replace%20all%20the%20alcohol%20with%20the%20nerdiest%20stuff%20you%20can%20imagine.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBankman-Fried%20and%20Yedidia%20lived%20and%20worked%20together%20in%20college%2C%20he%20testified.%20In%202017%2C%20he%20worked%20at%20Alameda%20Research%20for%20two%20months%20as%20a%20trader%20before%20leaving%20to%20pursue%20a%20PhD.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20he%20returned%20to%20working%20for%20Bankman-Fried%2C%20this%20time%20at%20FTX%20as%20a%20software%20developer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20became%20roommates%20once%20again.%20Yedidia%20said%20he%20lived%20in%20a%20%2435%20million%20penthouse%20apartment%20in%20the%20Bahamas%2C%20which%20he%20said%20Alameda%20Research%20purchased%20at%20Bankman-Fried's%20direction.%20Nine%20employees%20lived%20there%20in%20total%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYedida%20said%20he%20resigned%20from%20FTX%20in%20November%202022%20after%20he%20learned%20that%20Alameda%20Research%20used%20FTX%20customer%20funds%20to%20repay%20creditors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20was%20the%20last%20time%20he%20saw%20Bankman-Fried%20in%20person%2C%20he%20said%20%E2%80%94%20until%20testifying%20at%20his%20criminal%20trial.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYedidia%20took%20the%20stand%20following%20testimony%20from%20a%20former%20FTX%20customer%20who%20said%20he%20lost%20thousands%20of%20dollars%20by%20being%20unable%20to%20withdraw%20funds%20from%20the%20exchange%20at%20the%20time%20of%20its%20collapse.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20Wednesday%2C%20during%20opening%20statements%2C%20prosecutors%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-bankman-fried-lawyer-tries-pins-ftx-collapse-caroline-ellison-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epainted%20Bankman-Fried%20as%20a%20thief%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20stole%20over%20%2410%20billion%20from%20FTX%20customers%20while%20telling%20them%20they%20could%20access%20their%20money%20whenever%20they%20wanted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20defense%20said%20Bankman-Fried%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bmath%20nerd%26quot%3B%20who%20built%20two%20lucrative%20businesses%20in%20the%20span%20of%20a%20few%20years%20but%20overlooked%20some%20aspects%20of%20risk%20management.%20Bankman-Fried's%20fault%20was%20entrusting%20his%20executives%2C%20such%20as%20ex-girlfriend%20Caroline%20Ellison%2C%20to%20run%20the%20business%2C%20his%20attorney%20argued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-bankman-fried-trial-former-roommate-adam-yedidia-immunity-testimony-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696457750000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F651dd6d52ce014759e7534fa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22ori