Carthy's%20ouster%2C%20that%20%26quot%3Btraditional%20Republicans%26quot%3B%20should%20%26quot%3Bjoin%20us%20in%20partnership%20for%20the%20good%20of%20the%20country.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20dust%20settled%20after%20the%20vote%20to%20boot%20McCarthy%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20I%20spotted%20Republican%20Rep.%20Mike%20Lawler%20walking%20away%20from%20the%20Capitol.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELawler%20represents%20a%20New%20York%20district%20that%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20easily%20won%20in%202020%2C%20and%20he's%20postured%20as%20a%20reasonable%20deal-maker%20since%20coming%20to%20Congress.%20Biden%20himself%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ftherecount%2Fstatus%2F1656363559566077981%5C%22%3Eonce%20described%3C%2Fa%3E%20Lawler%20as%20%26quot%3Bnot%20one%20of%20these%20MAGA%20Republicans%2C%26quot%3B%20much%20to%20the%20horror%20of%20fellow%20Democrats.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20short%2C%20he's%20the%20exact%20type%20of%20Republican%20you%20might%20expect%20to%20cross%20the%20aisle%20in%20a%20%26quot%3Bcoalition%20government%26quot%3B%20deal%20scenario.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221777%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rep.%20Mike%20Lawler%20on%20a%20compromise%20speakership%3A%20%E2%80%9CYou%20can%20kiss%20that%20goodbye.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F651d9fcd2ce014759e74c6df%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERep.%20Mike%20Lawler%20on%20a%20compromise%20speakership%3A%20%E2%80%9CYou%20can%20kiss%20that%20goodbye.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ETom%20Williams%2FCQ-Roll%20Call%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20reporters%20peppered%20him%20with%20questions%20about%20what%20happens%20next%2C%20he%20tried%20to%20stay%20mum%2C%20declaring%20repeatedly%20that%20%26quot%3Bwe're%20gonna%20go%20to%20conference%20and%20have%20a%20discussion.%26quot%3B%20But%20when%20I%20posed%20the%20coalition%20idea%20to%20him%2C%20he%20suddenly%20snapped%20out%20o