2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fakasa-stops-flights-on-8-routes-reduces-services-on-10-other-routes-123100401179_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fakasa-stops-flights-on-8-routes-reduces-services-on-10-other-routes-123100401179_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fakasa-stops-flights-on-8-routes-reduces-services-on-10-other-routes-123100401179_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bihar%20Caste%20Survey%3A%20Why%20the%20BJP%20Is%20Jittery%20and%20INDIA%20Bloc%20Upbeat%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F17172239%2FSupporter_of_Bharatiya_Janata_Party_at_an_election_rally_in_Amethi.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20release%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbihar-caste-census-released-at-63-obc-ebc-groups-set-to-take-pole-position-in-state-politics%5C%22%3EBihar%20caste%20survey%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20is%20not%20only%20unnerved%20but%20also%20appears%20confused%20about%20how%20to%20respond%20to%20the%20issue.%20There%20has%20been%20a%20complete%20divergence%20between%20the%20stance%20taken%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20his%20Cabinet%20colleagues%20as%20well%20as%20senior%20leaders%20of%20his%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20announcement%20by%20Bihar%20chief%20minister%20Nitish%20Kumar%20that%20the%20full%20report%20would%20be%20out%20in%20one%20and%20a%20half%20months%20has%20made%20the%20BJP%20jittery.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnarendra-modi-caste-census-speech%5C%22%3Edescribed%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20survey%20report%20as%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Epaap%3C%2Fem%3E%20(sin)%20to%20divide%20the%20Hindu%20society%E2%80%9D%20and%20accused%20Congress%20of%20%E2%80%9Ctaking%20away%20the%20minorities%E2%80%99%20rights%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20Bihar%20chief%20minister%20called%20an%20all-party%20meeting%20on%20Tuesday%20to%20follow%20up%20on%20the%20survey%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20of%20now%2C%20the%20government%20has%20published%20the%20statistics%20of%20215%20castes%20in%20the%20state.%20It%20will%20table%20the%20statistics%20of%20the%20comprehensive%20economic%20survey%20report%20in%20the%20state%20Legislature%20after%20one%20and%20half%20months%2C%E2%80%9D%20Nitish%20said%20in%20a%20meeting%20with%20the%20representatives%20of%20nine%20parties%20from%20Bihar%2C%20including%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20(Nitish)%20might%20drop%20another%20bombshell%20with%20the%20economic%20survey%20report.%20Who%20knows%E2%80%A6%20he%20might%20break%20the%20cap%20of%2050%25%20quota%20in%20the%20jobs%20and%20raise%20the%20same%20for%20the%20backward%20classes%20and%20the%20extremely%20backward%20classes%20in%20Bihar%20beyond%20the%20existing%2027%25%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20a%20senior%20BJP%20leader%20who%20is%20unhappy%20with%20the%20prime%20minister%20reacting%20to%20the%20survey%20in%20an%20%E2%80%9Cunwise%E2%80%9D%20manner.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnine-reasons-why-the-bihar-caste-census-could-shake-up-national-politics%5C%22%3ENine%20Reasons%20Why%20Numbers%20Revealed%20by%20Bihar%20Caste%20Census%20Could%20Shake%20Up%20National%20Politics%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EApna%20Dal%20leader%20Anupirya%20Patel%2C%20who%20is%20a%20minister%20in%20the%20Modi%20government%2C%20has%20also%20extended%20her%20support%20to%20the%20idea%20of%20conducting%20a%20caste%20census%20nationwide.%20Her%20statement%20came%20at%20around%20the%20same%20time%20when%20Modi%20questioned%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20demand%20for%20a%20nationwide%20census%20at%20a%20public%20meeting%20in%20Jagdalpur%20in%20poll-bound%20Chhattisgarh.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESushil%20Kumar%20Modi%2C%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20senior%20leader%20in%20Bihar%20who%20is%20said%20to%20have%20a%20better%20understanding%20of%20the%20caste%20politics%20in%20the%20state%2C%20has%20tried%20to%20take%20credit%20for%20the%20caste%20survey.%20He%20said%20it%20was%20the%20BJP%20which%20had%20conceived%20the%20idea%20when%20it%20was%20in%20power%20in%20the%20state%20along%20with%20Nitish%20Kumar.%20Meanwhile%2C%20another%20BJP%20leader%20from%20the%20state%20and%20Union%20minister%20Giriraj%20Singh%20rubbished%20the%20report%20as%20%E2%80%9Ceyewash%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECoherent%20INDIA%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20prime%20minister%2C%20his%20ministers%2C%20and%20party%20colleagues%20sang%20different%20tunes%2C%20leaders%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20foregrounded%20the%20formula%20that%20a%20share%20in%20governance%20should%20be%20proportionate%20to%20the%20size%20of%20a%20community%E2%80%99s%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERahul%20Gandhi%2C%20soon%20after%20the%20publication%20of%20the%20report%2C%20tweeted%20that%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20(OBCs)%2C%20Scheduled%20Castes%20and%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20constituted%2084%25%20of%20the%20population.%20%E2%80%9COnly%20three%20out%20of%2090%20secretaries%20in%20the%20government%20of%20India%20belong%20to%20the%20OBCs%20who%20control%20barely%205%25%20of%20the%20budget.%20%3Cem%3EJitni%20aabadi%20utna%20haq%20%E2%80%93%20ye%20hamara%20pran%20hai%20%3C%2Fem%3E(rights%20according%20to%20the%20size%20of%20the%20population%20%3Cem%3E%20%E2%80%93%3C%2Fem%3E%20it%20is%20our%20resolve)%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20leader%E2%80%99s%20statement%20is%20perfectly%20in%20sync%20with%20that%20of%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20(RJD)%20president%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%E2%80%99s%20comment.%20He%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EJitni%20hissedari%20utni%20bhagidari%3C%2Fem%3E%20(participation%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20population).%E2%80%9D%20Even%20Samajwadi%20Party%20chief%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20supported%20the%20report%20released%20by%20the%20Bihar%20government%20and%20made%20a%20pitch%20for%20a%20similar%20exercise%20nationwide.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20survey%20report%2C%20OBCs%20and%20extremely%20backward%20castes%20(EBCs)%20constitute%2063%25%20of%20Bihar%E2%80%99s%20population.%20SCs%20account%20for%2019.65%25.%20The%20population%20of%20upper%20castes%20(general%20category)%20is%2015.52%25%2C%20which%20also%20includes%20about%205%25%20upper%20caste%20Muslims.%20Muslims%20altogether%20account%20for%2017.70%25%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20the%20numerical%20dominance%20of%20OBCs%20in%20the%20Hindi%20heartland%20that%20has%20given%20regional%20parties%20%E2%80%93%20RJD%20and%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%20in%20Bihar%3B%20and%20Samajwadi%20Party%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20%E2%80%93%20confidence.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20it%20has%20unnerved%20the%20BJP%2C%20given%20the%20thin%20population%20of%20the%20Hindu%20upper%20castes%20and%20the%20business%20communities%20%E2%80%93%20its%20primary%20support%20base.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F09%2F11121801%2Frepresentative-image.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22799%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F09%2F11121801%2Frepresentative-image.jpg%20799w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F09%2F11121801%2Frepresentative-image-300x143.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-551546%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22380%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERepresentative%20image.%20Photo%3A%20PTI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EMuch%20to%20the