0ties%20with%20the%20BJP%20in%20August%202022%2C%20brought%20the%20warring%20West%20Bengal%20and%20Delhi%20chief%20ministers%20%E2%80%93%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20and%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20%E2%80%93%20and%20the%20SP%20boss%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20to%20the%20table%20with%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F29182927%2FFtgenvMagAAmsB9final.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F29182927%2FFtgenvMagAAmsB9final.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F29182927%2FFtgenvMagAAmsB9final-300x151.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F29182927%2FFtgenvMagAAmsB9final-1024x516.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-655515%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22605%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EMallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20Nitish%20Kumar%20address%20the%20press%20after%20their%20meeting%20on%20April%2012%2C%202023.%20Photo%3A%20Twitter%2F%40RJDforIndia%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3ENitish%20flummoxed%20the%20BJP%20by%20doing%20so%2C%20as%20the%20Hindutva%20party%20had%20revelled%20when%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%2C%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%2C%20and%20SP%20had%20previously%20trained%20their%20guns%20at%20the%20Congress.%20Thanks%20to%20the%20Bihar%20chief%20minister%20playing%20as%20the%20key%20architect%2C%20these%20parties%20are%20now%20integral%20components%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20that%20has%20close%20to%2030%20parties%20%E2%80%93%20mostly%20with%20strong%20roots%20in%20states%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20obvious%20bid%20to%20score%20over%20INDIA%20holding%20its%20third%20conclave%20in%20Mumbai%20on%20August%2031%20and%20September%201%2C%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20announced%20a%20special%20session%20of%20parliament%20without%20revealing%20the%20agenda.%20After%20a%20lot%20of%20suspense%20over%20the%20agenda%2C%20the%20government%20introduced%20the%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Reservation%20Bill%20with%20the%20precondition%20that%20it%20would%20be%20implemented%20after%20conducting%20the%20census%20and%20a%20delimitation%20exercise.%20Media%20outlets%20supportive%20of%20the%20government%20described%20the%20move%20as%20yet%20another%20of%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cmasterstrokes%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-narendra-modi-social-justice-caste-census-obc-dalit%5C%22%3EHow%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Own%20Fragmenting%20of%20Social%20Justice%20Politics%20Led%20to%20the%20Bihar%20Caste%20Census%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20Nitish%20has%2C%20effectively%2C%20punctured%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20moves%20by%20bringing%20out%20the%20statistics%20of%20the%20caste-based%20survey.%20Now%2C%20the%20INDIA%20parties%20perceive%20Bihar%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9Cmicrocosm%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20larger%20demography%20in%20the%20Hindi%20heartland.%20As%20such%2C%20the%20caste%20survey%20will%20create%20a%20%E2%80%9Cnew%20consciousness%E2%80%9D%20among%20the%20OBCs%20%E2%80%93%20ushering%20in%20an%20era%20of%20Mandal%202.0%20in%20Bihar%20and%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20which%20account%20for%20125%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats.%20The%20BJP%20and%20its%20allies%20had%20won%20104%20of%20these%20in%20the%202019%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20it%20is%20because%20of%20his%20clout%20among%20the%20EBCs%20%E2%80%93%20who%20constitute%20about%2036.01%25%20of%20Bihar%E2%80%99s%20population%20%E2%80%93%20that%20Nitish%20has%20lasted%20for%20so%20long%20as%20the%20chief%20minister%20for%20nearly%20two%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20with%20the%20support%20of%20the%20EBCs%20that%20Nitish%20%E2%80%93%20in%20an%20alliance%20with%20the%20BJP%20%E2%80%93%20replaced%20the%20mighty%20Lalu-Rabri%20government%20in%202005.%20Be%20it%20the%20BJP%20or%20the%20RJD%2C%20he%20ensures%20the%20victory%20of%20his%20alliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20coming%20to%20power%20in%202005%2C%20Nitish%20increased%20his%20clout%20among%20the%20EBCs%20by%20giving%20them%2015%25%20quota%20against%2012%25%20to%20the%20BCs%20%E2%80%93%20a%20formula%20that%20Karpoori%20Thakur%20had%20implemented%20as%20the%20Bihar%20chief%20minister%20in%20the%201970s%20%E2%80%93%20in%20jobs%2C%20panchayats%20and%20other%20local%20bodies%2C%20and%20initiated%20a%20plethora%20of%20welfare%20schemes%20for%20the%20EBCs%20and%20Mahadalits.%20In%20the%20process%2C%20Nitish%20consolidated%20a%20large%20population%20of%20the%20poor.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20Bihar%2C%20the%20BJP%20will%20be%20up%20against%20an%20incredibly%20strong%20alliance.%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%20commands%20the%20unbreakable%20support%20of%20the%20Yadavs%20and%20Muslims%2C%20who%20together%20constitute%20nearly%2032%25%20of%20Bihar%E2%80%99s%20population%2C%20while%20Nitish%20Kumar%E2%80%99s%20core%20support%20base%20makes%20up%20another%20third%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20population.%20Add%20to%20this%20mix%20the%20left%20parties%20and%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20opposition%20will%20be%20in%20a%20commanding%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMany%20BJP%20insiders%20fear%20that%20the%20BJP%20will%20be%20decimated%20in%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20in%20Bihar.%20That%20is%20why%20the%20Hindutva%20party%20is%20nervous.%20And%20that%20is%20also%20precisely%20the%20reason%20for%20INDIA%E2%80%99s%20mirth.%20Almost%20all%20leaders%20of%20the%20INDIA%20parties%20feel%20that%20police%20raids%20on%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%20journalists%20on%20Tuesday%20are%20part%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20ploy%20to%20distract%20attention%20from%20Bihar%E2%80%99s%20caste%20survey.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENalin