P%20spokesperson%20Saurabh%20Bharadwaj%20%E2%80%93%20who%20was%20also%20present%20at%20the%20press%20conference%20%E2%80%93%20said%20that%20the%20actions%20of%20the%20BJP%20government%20over%20the%20past%20two%20days%20show%20that%20it%20knows%20that%20it%20is%20going%20to%20lose%20most%20of%20the%20five%20upcoming%20state%20elections%20(Telangana%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Mizoram)%20later%20this%20year%20and%20the%20general%20elections%20scheduled%20for%20next%20year.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20five%20state%20elections%20that%20are%20coming%20up%2C%20BJP%20is%20losing%20most%20of%20them.%20Those%20(television)%20channels%20that%20help%20the%20BJP%2C%20even%20they%20have%20not%20been%20able%20to%20help%20the%20BJP%20much%20in%20their%20opinion%20polls.%20The%20situation%20on%20the%20ground%20is%20very%20bad.%20They%20are%20trying%20to%20give%20reservations%20to%20women%2C%20make%20the%20prices%20of%20cylinders%20cheaper%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CYesterday%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20brave%20journalists%20who%20pose%20questions%20to%20the%20government%20were%20raided%20and%20questioned%20throughout%20the%20day%20and%20attempts%20were%20made%20to%20label%20them%20anti-nationals.%20And%20today%20the%20strongest%20voice%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20parliament%2C%20Sanjay%20Singh%20has%20been%20arrested%20without%20any%20evidence%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bharadwaj%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20said%20that%20this%20proves%20that%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20is%20desperate.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20all%20dictatorships%2C%20we%20have%20seen%20that%20such%20activities%20are%20done%20when%20there%20is%20a%20fear%20of%20losing%20power.%20But%20no%20one%20has%20held%20on%20to%20power%20by%20doing%20such%20acts.%20After%202024%2C%20we%20will%20be%20proved%20right%20that%20such%20acts%20will%20not%20bring%20any%20results.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEarlier%20in%20July%2C%20Singh%20was%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Faap-announces-nationwide-protest-against-sanjay-singhs-rajya-sabha-suspension-manipur-turmoil%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esuspended%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20from%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20for%20the%20entire%20monsoon%20session.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESingh%E2%80%99s%20Rajya%20Sabha%20colleague%20RJD%20MP%20Manoj%20Jha%20said%20that%20the%20Modi%20government%20is%20trying%20to%20instill%20fear%20in%20the%20opposition.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20this%20age%2C%20those%20who%20are%20scared%20will%20die.%20(%3Cem%3EJo%20dar%20gaya%20wo%20mar%20gaya%3C%2Fem%3E).%20The%20dictator%20himself%20is%20scared.%20And%20the%20results%20will%20be%20visible%20soon%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20this%20age%20of%20dictatorship%20one%20who%20fears%20is%20dead.%20The%20dictator%20is%20himself%20scared.%20And%20the%20result%20of%20this%20will%20be%20visible%20soon%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRJDforIndia%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40RJDforIndia%3C%2Fa%3E%20RS%20MP%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmanojkjhadu%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40manojkjhadu%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20the%20arrest%20of%20AAP%20RS%20MP%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FSanjaySingh%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23SanjaySingh%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20ED.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FcnSWHte4pS%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FcnSWHte4pS%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Anand%20Singh%20(%40Anand_Journ)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAnand_Journ%2Fstatus%2F1709562207564910919%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EOctober%204%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20BJP%20on%20the%20other%20han