%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fpakistan-warns-afghan-taliban-against-harboring-militants%2Fa-66240251%5C%22%3ETehreek-e-Taliban%20Pakistan%20(TTP)%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20a%20group%20with%20links%20to%20the%20hardline%C2%A0Taliban%C2%A0Sunni%20militants%20who%20retook%20power%20in%20Afghanistan%20two%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20TTP%20has%20said%20it%20wants%20to%20overthrow%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20government%20and%20rule%20with%20its%20strict%20interpretation%20of%20Islamic%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMillions%20of%20Afghans%20have%20entered%20Pakistan%20over%20the%20years%2C%20following%20successive%20wars%20and%20authoritarian%20regimes.%20Some%20600%2C000%20arrived%20since%20August%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMany%20Afghans%20are%20on%20waiting%20lists%20to%20get%20Pakistani%20visas%2C%20but%20the%20process%20can%20take%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWith%20inputs%20from%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fpakistan-orders-illegal-migrant-afghans-to-leave-country%2Fa-66988742%5C%22%3EDW%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696428944000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F04191718%2F49869773933_4581459b7d_k2.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fafghan-taliban-urges-pakistan-to-reconsider-ultimatum-to-undocumented-immigrants%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Pakistan's%20decision%20to%20expel%20undocumented%20immigrants%20came%20amid%20claims%20it%20made%20that%20a%20majority%20of%20suicide%20bombings%20in%20the%20country%20this%20year%20were%20carried%20out%20by%20Afghan%20nationals.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fafghan-taliban-urges-pakistan-to-reconsider-ultimatum-to-undocumented-immigrants%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Cricket%20Blues%3A%20%E2%80%98Is%20the%20World%20Cup%20Happening%20in%20India%3F%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F04190042%2FF7mLzKbXIAAOuC_.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%20is%20happening%20in%20India%3F%E2%80%9D%20asked%20my%20cousin%2C%20who%20is%20one%20of%20those%20people%20who%20say%2C%20%E2%80%98I%20do%20not%20watch%20cricket%2C%20but%20I%20follow%20the%20World%20Cup.%E2%80%99%20Although%20he%20does%20not%20pay%20much%20attention%20to%20cricket%2C%20my%20cousin%20was%20taken%20aback%20that%20he%20was%20not%20aware%20that%20India%20was%20hosting%20the%2050-over%20or%20ODI%20Cricket%20World%20Cup.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20cousin%E2%80%99s%20surprise%20about%20who%20is%20hosting%20the%20World%20Cup%20is%20not%20his%20fault%20alone.%20There%20are%20enough%20reasons%20to%20believe%20that%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%202023%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%20has%20been%20underwhelming.%20From%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbesindia.com%2Farticle%2Fnews%2Fthe-impossible-task-of-buying-tickets-for-the-2023-cricket-world-cup%2F88061%2F1%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20impossible%20task%20of%20buying%20match%20tickets%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwisden.com%2Fseries-stories%2Fcricket-world-cup-2023%2Fa-complete-fiasco-bcci-icc-slammed-for-2023-cricket-world-cup-fixture-change-scandal%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Efiasco%20involving%20a%20last-minute%20change%20of%20venues%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20an%20increasing%20sentiment%20that%20the%2050-over%20format%20has%20become%20%E2%80%9Credundant%E2%80%9D%20among%20new%20audiences%20%E2%80%93%20who%20have%20made%20IPL%20the%20number%20one%20cricket%20tournament.%20The%202023%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%20does%20not%20carry%20the%20same%20charm%20it%20did%20back%20in%202011%20%E2%80%93%20when%20India%20last%20hosted%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFading%20relevance%20of%2050-over%20cricket%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGaurav%20Kapur%2C%20the%20mainstream%20face%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20cricket%20broadcast%2C%20admitted%20that%20the%2050-over%20format%20is%20the%20%E2%80%9Cmost%20boring%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Csoon%20to%20be%20redundant%E2%80%9D%20on%20the%20Grade%20Cricketer%20podcast%20on%20YouTube.%20He%20spoke%20about%20the%20%E2%80%9Cpointless%E2%80%9D%20three-match%20ODI%20series%20losing%20their%20importance.%20Kapur%20summarised%20the%20opinion%20of%20those%20who%20want%20to%20do%20away%20with%20the%2050-over%20format%20as%20such%3A%20only%20the%20first%2010%20and%20the%20last%2010%20overs%20of%20an%20ODI%20match%20interest%20the%20audience%3B%20the%20overs%20in%20between%20are%20like%20%E2%80%9Ca%20government%20job%E2%80%9D%2C%20where%20the%20batting%20side%20and%20bowling%20side%20take%20it%20easy%20and%20agree%20to%20go%20at%20a%20run%20rate%20of%20five%20runs%20per%20over.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20a%20personal%20level%2C%20I%20do%20not%20agree%20with%20the%20opinion%20that%20ODI%20cricket%20must%20be%20done%20away%20with.%20But%20one%20cannot%20look%20away%20from%20what%20is%20unfolding.%20With%20the%20constant%20bombardment%20of%20T20%20cricket%20and%20the%20fast-paced%20nature%20of%20the%20IPL%20and%20other%20similar%20tournaments%2C%20the%20game%20of%20cricket%20has%20changed%20a%20lot%20since%20the%20early%202000s.%20The%20new%20audiences%20want%20to%20watch%20sixes%20and%20fours%20or%20quick%205-wicket%20hauls%20%E2%80%93%20if%20there%20are%20still%20any%20fans%20of%20bowling.%20Patience%20for%20a%2050-over%20match%20is%20diminishing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%2C%20Ranveer%20Singh%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20past%2C%20World%20Cup%20theme%20songs%20have%20been%20used%20to%20drum%20up%20anticipation%20for%20the%20tournament.%20I%20remember%20the%202011%20World%20Cup%20theme%20song%2C%20%E2%80%98De%20Ghuma%20Ke%E2%80%99%2C%20playing%20on%20almost%20every%20channel%20for%20weeks%20before%20the%20games%20began.%20The%202023%20edition%E2%80%99s%20theme%20song%2C%20%E2%80%98Dil%20Jashn%20Bole%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20composed%20by%20Pritam%20and%20starring%20Ranveer%20Singh%20on%20an%20animated%20train%20%E2%80%93%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20gone%20down%20too%20well%20with%20cricket%20fans.%20The%20top%20comment%20regarding%20the%20song%2C%20shared%20on%20the%20ICC%E2%80%99s%20official%20YouTube%20channel%2C%20perhaps%20sums%20up%20the%20feeling%3A%20%E2%80%9CThis%20song%20hits%20different%20on%20mute.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FJhIBqykjzbs%3Fsi%3Dobttjqr_OhaefkqA%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20previous%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%20songs%20featured%20the%20sport%2C%20this%20time%20around%20it%20felt%20like%20watching%20a%20Bollywood%20movie%20song%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%93%20filled%20with%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Edancers%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ehaving%20zero%20regard%20for%20the%20other%20teams%20that%20are%20competing%20in%20the%20tournament.%20For%20example%2C%20how%20is%20a%20cricket%20fan%20in%20Cape%20Town%20expected%20to%20relate%20to%20%E2%80%98Dil%20Jashn%20Bole%E2%80%99%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHonestly%2C%20it%20is%20not%20just%20the%20song.%20The%20run-up%20to%20this%20World%20Cup%20seems%20pretty%20dry.%20The%20Board%20of%20Control%20for%20Cricket%20in%20India%20(BCCI)%20which%20is%20often%2C%20in%20a%20derogatory%20way%2C%20labelled%20to%20be%20an%20event%20management%20company%2C%20does%20not%20look%20comfortable%20managing%20this%20mega%20sports%20event.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20%E2%80%98impossible%E2%80%99%20task%20of%20buying%20tickets%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPlanning%20to%20watch%20a%20cricket%20match%20requires%20a%20lot%20of%20planning.%20First%2C%20you%20need%20to%20purchase%20a%20match%20ticket%20and%20second%2C%20a%20flight%20or%20train%20ticket%20to%20travel%20to%20the%20host%20city.%20The%20BCCI%20has%20made%20both%20tasks%20incredibly%20difficult.%20First%2C%20nine%20games%20were%20rescheduled%2C%20accounting%20for%20one-sixth%20of%20all%20group-stage%20matches%2C%20including%20the%20highly%20anticipated%20first-round%20match%20between%20India%20and%20Pakistan.%20England%2C%20the%20reigning%20World%20Cup%20champions%2C%20were%20worst%20affected%20%E2%80%93%20three%20out%20of%20their%20nine%20matches%20were%20rearranged.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESecond%2C%20only%20a%20limited%20number%20of%20match%20tickets%20were%20made%20available%20on%20the%20BookMyShow%20website.%20Fans%20complained%20about%20the%20harrowing%20experience%20of%20attempting%20to%20purchase%20tickets%20for%20the%20main%20event.%20They%20reported%20hours-long%20waits%20in%20online%20queues%20and%20claimed%20that%20tickets%20were%20already%20%E2%80%98sold%20out%E2%80%99%20before%20the%20official%20sale%20even%20commenced.%20To%20put%20things%20in%20perspective%2C%20only%208%2C500%20tickets%20were%20made%20available%20for%20the%20India-Pakistan%20game%20at%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20Stadium%20%E2%80%93%20which%20has%20the%20capacity%20to%20seat%20more%20than%201.3%20lakh%20people.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CEither%20the%20ticket%20partners%20are%20incompetent%20to%20handle%20the%20ticket%20and%20traffic%20or%20this%20is%20another%20eyewash%20in%20the%20name%20of%20releasing%20tickets.%20Hope%20there%20is%20a%20proper%20audit%20and%20identification%20of%20how%20the%20tickets%20are%20sold%20and%20to%20whom%20and%20what%20platform%2C%E2%80%9D%20wrote%20former%20cricketer%20Venkatesh%20Prasad%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENot%20finding%20tickets%20or%20mismanagement%20is%20one%20thing%2C%20but%20the%20real%20problem%20of%20the%20BCCI%2C%20as%20sports%20journalist%20Sharda%20Urga%20%E2%80%93%20who%20hosts%20the%20programme%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EOut%20of%20the%20Park%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98s%20YouTube%20channel%20%E2%80%93%20writes%2C%20is%20that%20%E2%80%9Cits%20core%20is%20hollowed%20out%20by%20abuse%20and%20exploitation%20of%20domestic%20players%20across%20age%20and%20gender%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F3fdrQrjAO4w%3Fsi%3D834AqjLWZfDU-LcC%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98BJP%E2%80%99s%20Control%20of%20Cricket%20in%20India%E2%80%99%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20above%20statement%20was%20part%20of%20Sharda%20Urga%E2%80%99s%20September%202023%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcaravanmagazine.in%2Fsports%2Fbjp-bcci-jay-shah%5C%22%3Ecover%20story%20for%20the%3Cem%3E%20Caravan%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20magazine.%20At%20the%20heart%20of%20this%20story%20is%20the%20new%20revenue%20model%20of%20the%20International%20Cricket%20Council%20(ICC).%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20meeting%20that%20concluded%20on%20July%2013%20this%20year%2C%20the%20BCCI%20secured%20a%20significant%20increase%20in%20its%20share%20of%20ICC%E2%80%99s%20annual%20earnings%2C%20which%20totals%20%24600%20million%20dollars%20for%20the%20cycle%20between%202024%20and%202027.%20The%20Indian%20board%E2%80%99s%20share%20has%20risen%20by%20a%20staggering%2072%25%2C%20resulting%20in%20an%20estimated%20earning%20of%20about%20%24230%20million%2C%20accounting%20for%2038.5%25%20of%20ICC%E2%80%99s%20new%20financial%20model%20for%20the%20next%20cycle.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20comparison%2C%20other%20cricket%20boards%20are%20far%20behind.%20The%20England%20and%20Wales%20Cricket%20Board%20(ECB)%20and%20Cricket%20Australia%20(CA)%20will%20earn%20single-digit%20percentages%2C%20specifically%206.89%25%20(%2441%20million)%20and%206.25%25%20(%2437.53%20million)%20respectively.%20The%20Pakistan%20Cricket%20Board%20(PCB)%20is%20fourth%20on%20the%20list%2C%20earning%205.75%25%20(%2434.51%20million)%20of%20the%20total%20earnings.%20The%20former%20ICC%20president%20Ehsan%20Mani%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fsites%2Ftristanlavalette%2F2023%2F05%2F12%2Fcashed-up-indias-wealth-and-power-should-be-reduced-says-former-pakistan-cricket-boss%2F%3Fsh%3D65dd2c713730%5C%22%3Etold%20%3Cem%3EForbes%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20new%20model%20would%20be%20%E2%80%9Cgiving%20the%20most%20money%20to%20the%20country%20that%20needs%20it%20the%20least.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20former%20England%20cricketer%20Michael%20Atherton%20expressed%20his%20displeasure%20towards%20this%20new%20revenue%20model.%20Writing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thetimes.co.uk%2Farticle%2Ficc-distribution-model-rich-nations-richer-mike-atherton-fsbz50mgb%5C%22%3Efor%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thetimes.co.uk%2Farticle%2Ficc-distribution-model-rich-nations-richer-mike-atherton-fsbz50mgb%5C%22%3EThe%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20a%20deeper%20malaise%20at%20work%20here.%20The%20economic%20transformation%20of%20India%20in%20the%20past%20three%20decades%20and%20the%20growing%20importance%20of%20television%20revenues%20have%20distorted%20cricket%E2%80%99s%20landscape%2C%20making%20it%20more%20unequal.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOther%20than%20that%2C%20there%20has%20been%20no%20regard%20for%20the%20recommendations%20given%20by%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Flodha-panel-report-top-10-recommendations%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20Supreme%20Court-appointed%20Lodha%20Committee%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20The%20most%20significant%20recommendation%20was%20that%20no%20office%20bearer%20can%20have%20two%20consecutive%20terms%20in%20office%20%E2%80%93%20but%20despite%20that%2C%20Jay%20Shah%2C%20the%20secretary%20of%20BCCI%20and%20the%20son%20of%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20has%20remained%20in%20the%20position%20for%20more%20than%20four%20years%20now.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20made%20possible%20when%20in%20September%202022%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindubusinessline.com%2Fnews%2Fsports%2Fsc-modifies-bccis-constitution-ganguly-and-jay-shah-to-continue-in-office%2Farticle65890174.ece%5C%22%3Eallowed%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20BCCI%20to%20make%20amendments%20to%20its%20constitution.%20Subsequently%2C%20any%20BCCI%20office-bearer%20can%20serve%20up%20to%2012%20years%20in%20the%20same%20post%2C%20without%20any%20cooling-off%20period%20between%20two%20terms%20in%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESharda%20Urga%20highlights%20the%20glaring%20irregularities%20within%20the%20BCCI%20in%20detail.%20From%20the%20bullying%20of%20the%20PCB%20over%20the%20scheduling%20of%20the%20Asia%20Cup%20to%20the%20changing%20of%20three%20kit%20sponsors%20in%20a%20short%20span%2C%20Jay%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20BCCI%20has%20acted%20as%20an%20extended%20arm%20of%20the%20government%20of%20India%2C%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fneeraj-kumar-cricket-bcci-corruption%5C%22%3EIn%20a%20Tell-All%20on%20Corruption%20in%20Cricket%2C%20Ex-IPS%20Officer%20Neeraj%20Kumar%20Hurls%20a%20Few%20Bouncers%20at%20Vinod%20Rai%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%9CSone%20Ki%20Chidiya%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20senior%20cricket%20journalist%2C%20Chander%20Shekhar%20Luthra%2C%20told%20me%20in%202021%2C%20%E2%80%9CYou%20cannot%20look%20at%20cricket%20and%20corruption%20separately.%E2%80%9D%20By%20that%2C%20he%20did%20not%20only%20mean%20instances%20like%20that%20of%20spot-fixing%20but%20also%20the%20brazen%20outlook%20of%20modern-day%20cricket%20as%20solely%20an%20instrument%20of%20money-making.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202015%2C%20BCCI%20president%20Shashank%20Manohar%20commissioned%20an%20audit%20by%20the%20British%20firm%20Deloitte%20Touche%20Tohmatsu%20to%20scrutinise%2027%20state%20cricket%20associations.%20His%20aim%20was%20to%20investigate%20discrepancies%2C%20as%20despite%20equal%20funding%2C%20some%20associations%20were%20facing%20financial%20challenges.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERamachandra%20Guha%2C%20a%20historian%20who%20was%20one%20of%20the%20three%20members%20chosen%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20to%20clean%20up%20the%20BCCI%2C%20documented%20this%20in%20his%20book%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Commonwealth%20of%20Cricket%3C%2Fem%3E.%20According%20to%20Guha%2C%20the%20audit%20revealed%20disturbing%20findings%2C%20including%20mismanagement.%20Examples%20ranged%20from%20extravagant%20purchases%20like%2018%20cars%2C%20dubious%20accounting%20methods%2C%20misuse%20of%20funds%20to%20buy%20flats%20for%20officials%2C%20false%20travel%20reimbursements%2C%20and%20even%20agricultural%20activities%20persisting%20on%20land%20meant%20for%20constructing%20cricket%20stadiums.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.outlookindia.com%2Fwebsite%2Fstory%2Fdeloitte-audit-report-exposes-financial-mess-in-bcci-affiliates%2F298162%5C%22%3Efindings%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20audit%20were%20so%20stark%20that%20the%20report%20was%20kept%20confidential%20%E2%80%93%20emphasising%20the%20scale%20of%20financial%20irregularities%20in%20state%20associations.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELet%20me%20explain%20this%20by%20giving%20the%20example%20of%20the%20Delhi%20%26amp%3B%20District%20Cricket%20Association%20(DDCA).%20Amongst%20all%20cricket%20boards%2C%20the%20DDCA%20has%20been%20considered%20the%20most%20opaque%20of%20all%20the%20cricket%20boards%20in%20the%20country.%20Questions%20were%20raised%20in%202000%20by%20an%20%3Cem%3EOutlook%3C%2Fem%3E%20magazine%20report%20suggesting%20that%20some%20members%20used%20proxy%20voting%20during%20internal%20board%20elections.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFormer%20cricketer%20Kirti%20Azad%20questions%20why%20the%20DDCA%20and%20other%20state%20associations%20can%E2%80%99t%20utilise%20their%20funds%20and%20facilities%20to%20establish%20training%20centres.%20He%20points%20out%20the%20prevalence%20of%20private%20academies%20which%20charge%20high%20fees%20for%20coaching%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20system%20where%20influential%20individuals%20can%20get%20their%20children%20selected%20through%20personal%20selectors.%20Azad%20alleges%20that%20the%20BCCI%20makes%20allocation%20of%20funds%20to%20states%20in%20mysterious%20ways%20which%20he%20likens%20to%20the%20%E2%80%9Cmystery%20of%20the%20Bermuda%20Triangle%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDomestic%20cricketers%20alerted%20me%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20there%20are%20no%20records%20for%20local%20DDCA%20tournaments.%20%E2%80%9CI%20scored%201%2C400%20runs%20in%2015%20matches%20in%20the%20league%20and%20still%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20selected%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20a%20domestic%20cricketer%2C%20who%20wishes%20to%20be%20anonymous.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20there%20are%20no%20records%2C%20on%20what%20basis%20are%20players%20selected%3F%20This%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20environment%20gives%20room%20for%20nepotism%20and%20corruption.%20%E2%80%9CI%20know%20a%20player%20who%20paid%20Rs%2036%20lakhs%20to%20get%20in%20the%20domestic%20team%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20domestic%20cricketer%20alleged.%20The%20same%20player%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20been%20able%20to%20score%20a%20century%20despite%20batting%20in%20the%20top%20order%20for%20Delhi%20for%20three%20years.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F12%2F21174235%2FScreen-Shot-2021-12-21-at-5.42.18-PM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22745%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F12%2F21174235%2FScreen-Shot-2021-12-21-at-5.42.18-PM.png%20745w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F12%2F21174235%2FScreen-Shot-2021-12-21-at-5.42.18-PM-300x151.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-571754%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22375%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20The%20Wire%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERich%20league%2C%20poor%20players%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fwatch-rich-league-poor-players-ipl-underpaid%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereports%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20showed%20that%20the%20IPL%20pays%20just%2018%25%20of%20its%20total%20revenue%20to%20players%20%E2%80%93%20a%20lower%20percentage%20than%20what%20the%20BCCI%20allocates%20to%20its%20players%20(26%25%20of%20gross%20revenue).%20Unlike%20other%20major%20sports%20leagues%2C%20the%20IPL%20does%20not%20follow%20the%20principle%20that%20players%20should%20earn%20at%20least%20half%20of%20the%20league%E2%80%99s%20revenue.%20For%20instance%2C%20the%20English%20Premier%20League%20allocates%2071%25%20of%20its%20total%20revenue%20to%20football%20players%2C%20while%20American%20baseball%2C%20basketball%2C%20ice%20hockey%2C%20and%20rugby%20leagues%20pay%20players%20around%2050%25%20of%20their%20total%20revenue.%20This%20highlights%20a%20significant%20disparity%20in%20revenue-sharing%20practices%20between%20the%20IPL%20and%20other%20major%20sports%20leagues.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20things%20get%20worse%20at%20the%20domestic%20level.%20Sharda%20Urga%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3ECaravan%3C%2Fem%3E%20article%20points%20out%20that%20the%20BCCI%20money%20distribution%20system%20reveals%20issues%20of%20accountability%20in%20states%20where%20funds%20are%20distributed%20and%20highlights%20the%20stark%20income%20disparity%20faced%20by%20domestic%20cricketers.%20One%20example%20cited%20a%20domestic%20cricketer%20earning%20an%20average%20of%20Rs%207.5%20lakh%20per%20season%2C%20with%20earnings%20fluctuating%20widely%20from%20season%20to%20season.%20The%20disparity%20in%20income%20poses%20significant%20challenges%20for%20domestic%20players%2C%20especially%20those%20not%20part%20of%20the%20international%20or%20IPL%20elite%2C%20leading%20to%20financial%20instability%20and%20uncertainty%20in%20their%20cricketing%20careers.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECricket%2C%20alas%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20all%20things%20said%20and%20done%2C%20the%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%2C%20with%20all%20its%20flaws%2C%20will%20continue%20to%20garner%20love%20and%20attention.%20At%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20the%20sport%20will%20continue%20to%20have%20passionate%20fans.%20Only%20the%20actions%20of%20the%2022%20players%20on%20the%20field%20will%20matter%20to%20the%20fans%2C%20not%20what%20happens%20outside%20of%20it.%20It%20will%20be%20the%20historic%20moments%20and%20performances%20that%20will%20be%20remembered%20%E2%80%93%20unlike%3C%2Fspan%3E%20the%20present%20India%20regime%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20delay%20visas%20for%20Pakistani%20players.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696428055000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F04190042%2FF7mLzKbXIAAOuC_.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fcricket-blues-is-the-world-cup-happening-in-india%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20world%20cup%20gets%20underway%20on%20October%205.%20For%20a%20cricket-obsessed%20nation%2C%20this%20should%20feel%20like%20going%20to%20the%20moon.%20But%20does%20it%20not%20quite%20feel%20that%20way%3F%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fcricket-blues-is-the-world-cup-happening-in-india%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pune%20Doctor%E2%80%99s%20AI-Powered%20Mobile%20Tool%20Screens%20%26amp%3B%20Detects%20Tuberculosis%20In%20a%20Few%20Seconds%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20major%20concerns%20in%20many%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F97795%2Fvolunteering-india-developingcountry-travelling-voluntourism%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edeveloping%20countries%3C%2Fa%3E%20such%20as%20India%20and%20Bangladesh%20is%20Tuberculosis.%20According%20to%20reports%2C%20approximately%2010%20million%20people%20fall%20ill%20yearly%20with%20infectious%20diseases.%20However%2C%20only%206%20million%20cases%20are%20identified%2C%20with%20the%20remaining%204%20million%20being%20%E2%80%9Cmissing%E2%80%9D%2C%20which%20means%20that%20they%20are%20either%20undiagnosed%2C%20untreated%20or%20go%20unreported%20to%20the%20healthcare%20systems.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20report%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20states%2C%20%E2%80%9CWith%20TB%20cases%20among%20children%20less%20than%2015%20years%20in%20India%20estimated%20to%20be%203%2C42%2C000%20every%20year%2C%20the%20detection%20of%20only%201%2C35%2C734%20children%20in%202022%20would%20mean%20that%20over%202%2C00%2C000%20(60%25)%20children%20with%20TB%20were%20missed%20last%20year%20alone.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20underlines%20a%20significant%20gap%20in%20the%20healthcare%20system.%20Dr%20Arun%20Chowdary%20Kotaru%2C%20a%20seasoned%20consultant%20in%20Respiratory%2FPulmonology%20and%20Sleep%20Medicine%20at%20the%20Artemis%20Hospital%2C%20Gurgaon%2C%20provides%20insight%20into%20this%20issue%2C%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CMany%20patients%20go%20undiagnosed%20or%20%E2%80%98missing%E2%80%99%20because%20the%20traditional%20testing%20system%20takes%20weeks%20to%20produce%20results%2C%20making%20it%20difficult%20to%20reach%20patients%20promptly.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERecognising%20the%20crucial%20time%20lag%20between%20testing%20and%20receiving%20test%20results%2C%20a%20Pune-based%20startup%20called%20DeepTek%20has%20developed%20a%20technology%20claiming%20to%20identify%20tuberculosis%20cases%20within%20seconds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDr%20Amit%20Kharat%2C%20the%20co-founder%20of%20DeepTek%2C%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9COnce%20patients%20undergo%20an%20X-ray%2C%20our%20AI-based%20model%2C%20Genki%2C%20scans%20the%20reports%20and%20identifies%20any%20signs%20of%20TB%20(abnormalities)%20within%2030%20to%2060%20seconds.%20Radiologists%20can%20then%20thoroughly%20review%20the%20reports%20to%20confirm%20the%20presence%20of%20the%20infection%2C%20a%20process%20that%20previously%20would%20have%20taken%20weeks.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20remarkable%20potential%20of%20this%20technology%2C%20we%20had%20a%20bunch%20of%20questions%20regarding%20its%20function.%20In%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20Dr%20Amit%20clarified%20all%20our%20doubts.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EAiming%20to%20make%20India%20TB%20free%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20three%20major%20concerns%20that%20arose%20when%20our%20conversation%20with%20Dr%20Amit%20began%20were%20%E2%80%93%20How%20does%20the%20technology%20work%3F%20What%20is%20its%20accuracy%3F%20And%20how%20can%20it%20reach%20the%20last%20mile%20in%20India%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnswering%20how%20the%20technology%20works%2C%20Dr%20Amit%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20first%20started%20researching%20on%20how%20artificial%20intelligence%20(AI)%20can%20be%20used%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F284072%2Fsynapsica-radiologist-ai-mri-technology-imaging-accurate-report-diagnoses%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efield%20of%20radiology%2C%20I%3C%2Fa%3E%20found%20that%20TB%20is%20a%20huge%20challenge%20and%20the%20government%20is%20looking%20for%20new-age%20solutions%20to%20eliminate%20this%20disease.%20This%20is%20how%20our%20journey%20started%20in%20the%20TB%20scanning%20space%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fgrowclub-5-1696427075.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20AI%20was%20developed%20using%20more%20than%2010%20million%20data%20points%20from%20various%20sources%20and%20places%20in%20the%20world.%20%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fgrowclub-5-1696427075.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fgrowclub-5-1696427075-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fgrowclub-5-1696427075-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fgrowclub-5-1696427075-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fgrowclub-5-1696427075-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-331550%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20AI%20was%20developed%20using%20more%20than%2010%20million%20data%20points%20from%20various%20sources%20and%20places%20in%20the%20world.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20DeepTek%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20a%20stigma%20around%20TB%20and%20in%20most%20cases%2C%20patients%20do%20not%20come%20to%20doctors%20till%20their%20illness%20becomes%20very%20serious.%20By%20this%20time%2C%20since%20the%20disease%20spreads%20through%20cough%20droplets%2C%20the%20patient%20has%20most%20likely%20affected%20more%20people%20in%20the%20area.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20reaches%20these%20areas%20to%20scan%20for%20more%20cases%20of%20TB.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20camps%20set%20up%20and%20vans%20reach%20rural%20areas%20to%20do%20X-rays%20of%20these%20people.%20However%2C%20once%20the%20X-ray%20is%20done%2C%20it%20needs%20to%20be%20sent%20to%20a%20radiology%20department%20for%20study.%20This%20takes%20a%20lot%20of%20time%2C%20making%20it%20difficult%20to%20reach%20the%20suspected%20patients%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20where%20Genki%20comes%20in%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20chest%20X-rays%20are%20scanned%20by%20the%20AI%20and%20within%20seconds%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20CPU%20setting%20and%20core%20capacity%20of%20the%20system%20in%20the%20van%2C%20camp%20or%20hospital%2C%20the%20reports%20come%20in%20within%2060%20seconds.%20This%20way%20the%20patient%20can%20be%20informed%20and%20taken%20to%20treatment%20then%20and%20there%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20a%20sputum%20test%20can%20be%20done%20to%20confirm%20the%20presence%20of%20infection%20in%20the%20patient.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEarlier%2C%20what%20used%20to%20happen%20was%20that%20once%20the%20patient%20was%20diagnosed%2C%20a%20healthcare%20worker%20deported%20by%20the%20government%20would%20find%20them%20and%20then%20take%20them%20for%20further%20testing.%20This%20would%20cost%20the%20government%20unnecessary%20expenses.%20Additionally%2C%20all%20the%20suspected%20cases%20had%20to%20undergo%20a%20Genexpert%20Test%20after%20an%20X-ray%20which%20is%20a%20costly%20affair%20for%20the%20government.%20Now%2C%20with%20Genki%2C%20not%20every%20patient%20has%20to%20go%20through%20the%20test%20but%20only%20the%20ones%20detected%20by%20the%20AI%20have%20to%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20has%20not%20only%20reduced%20the%20time%20lag%20between%20testing%20and%20results%20but%20also%20reduced%20the%20cost%20for%20the%20government.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20its%20accuracy%2C%20Amit%20explains%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F199904%2Fmumbai-startup-tb-artificial-intelligence-innovation-tuberculosis-diagnosis-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20AI%20was%20developed%3C%2Fa%3E%20using%20more%20than%2010%20million%20data%20points%20from%20various%20sources%20and%20places%20in%20the%20world.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CChest%20X-ray%20data%20points%20are%20easily%20available%20for%20research%20purposes.%20We%20have%20also%20collaborated%20with%20medical%20schools%20and%20hospitals%20for%20research%20and%20collecting%20data.%20We%20have%20been%20audited%20by%20Stop%20TB%2C%20a%20WHO%20body%20which%20has%20given%20a%20green%20signal%20calling%20our%20AI%E2%80%99s%20results%20as%20good%20as%20human%20reading%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20838px)%20100vw%2C%20838px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fgrowclub-7-1696427069.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dr%20Amit%20Kharat%20and%20Dr%20Ajit%20Patel%2C%20co-founders%20of%20DeepTek%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22838%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fgrowclub-7-1696427069.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fgrowclub-7-1696427069-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fgrowclub-7-1696427069-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fgrowclub-7-1696427069-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fgrowclub-7-1696427069-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-331548%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDr%20Amit%20Kharat%20and%20Dr%20Ajit%20Patel%2C%20co-founders%20of%20DeepTek.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20DeepTek%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20technology%20was%20initially%20used%20in%20Greater%20Chennai%20Corporation%20and%20has%20expanded%20to%208%20districts%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20screened%20more%20than%20300%2C000%20patients%20in%20totality.%20Moreover%2C%20we%20have%20moved%20to%20Puducherry%20and%20Thane%20municipal%20corporation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBesides%20India%2C%20AI%20is%20working%20in%20countries%20like%20Bangladesh%2C%20the%20Philippines%2C%20Mongolia%2C%20and%20Thailand.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20approval%20from%20the%20United%20States%20of%20America%E2%80%99s%20FDA%20and%20we%20recently%20received%20approval%20from%20an%20Indian%20regulatory%20body%20called%20Central%20Drugs%20Standard%20Control%20Organisation%20(CDSCO)%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20how%20Genki%20can%20help%20the%20government%20reach%20the%20remotest%20areas%20of%20the%20country%20and%20eliminate%20TB%2C%20Dr%20Amit%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWith%20newer%20innovations%2C%20the%20X-ray%20machines%20have%20become%20so%20small%20and%20easy%20to%20carry%20that%20a%20person%20can%20take%20it%20to%20the%20remotest%20of%20places.%20Combined%20with%20Genki%2C%20any%20nodal%20officer%20can%20easily%20locate%20patients%20and%20get%20their%20sputum%20samples.%20All%20this%20can%20be%20done%20with%20a%20push%20of%20a%20few%20buttons.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDeeptek%20started%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F59851%2Ftuberculosis-xdr-10-km-run%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETB%20scanning%3C%2Fa%3E%20but%20now%20has%20evolved%20into%20various%20other%20branches%20too.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20evolved%20in%20the%20years.%20Today%2C%20we%20have%20products%20such%20as%20a%20patient%20tool%20that%20works%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20a%20cloud%20platform%20which%20records%20the%20data%20of%20patients%20with%20access%20to%2030%2B%20AIs%20and%20a%20responsible%20AI%20threshold%20that%20regulates%20the%20accuracy%20of%20the%20AI%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20the%20future%2C%20Dr%20Amit%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20to%20work%20with%20NGOs%20and%20the%20government%20and%20be%20a%20part%20in%20helping%20them%20eliminate%20TB%20at%20the%20national%20level.%20With%20the%20help%20of%20AI%2C%20we%20have%20the%20ability%20to%20reach%20the%20last%20mile%20and%20bring%20an%20end%20to%20this%20illness.%20With%20all%20these%20innovations%20I%20feel%20like%20TB%20is%20something%20that%20can%20be%20uprooted%20and%20removed%20from%20the%20country.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EExperts%20speak%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3ETo%20understand%20better%20the%20need%20for%20such%20a%20tool%2C%20we%20spoke%20to%20several%20experts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDr%20Arun%20Chowdary%20Kotaru%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CTools%20like%20Genki%2C%20which%20claim%20to%20use%20AI%20to%20detect%20TB%20in%20a%20few%20seconds%20using%20digital%20chest%20radiographs%2C%20have%20the%20potential%20to%20be%20immensely%20helpful.%20Faster%20diagnosis%20means%20early%20initiation%20of%20treatment%2C%20which%20is%20important%20for%20controlling%20TB%E2%80%99s%20spread%20and%20improving%20patient%20outcomes.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CGenki%20can%20be%20deployed%20in%20regions%20with%20limited%20access%20to%20healthcare%20facilities%20or%20expert%20radiologists.%20This%20can%20extend%20diagnostic%20capabilities%20to%20underserved%20areas%2C%20helping%20to%20diagnose%20TB%20cases%20that%20might%20otherwise%20go%20unnoticed%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Arun%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fgrowclub-6-1696427072.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fgrowclub-6-1696427072.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fgrowclub-6-1696427072-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fgrowclub-6-1696427072-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fgrowclub-6-1696427072-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fgrowclub-6-1696427072-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-331549%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20AI%20has%20already%20scanned%20over%20three%20lakh%20patients%20in%20India.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20DeepTek%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%20%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20along%20similar%20lines%2C%20Dr%20Nimish%20Shah%2C%20consultant%2C%20Respiratory%20Medicine%2C%20Jaslok%20Hospital%20%26amp%3B%20Research%20Centre%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWith%20the%20overall%20TB%20burden%20we%20face%2C%20there%20is%20always%20scope%20for%20improvement%20and%20using%20tools%20to%20enhance%20efficiency.%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F308446%2Fhyderabad-health-tech-startup-swaasa-ai-software-helps-detect-lung-disease-tb-detection%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20AI%20can%20help%20send%20alerts%3C%2Fa%3