sion%20%26amp%3B%20Face%20My%20Demons%3B%20It%20Can%20Help%20You%20Too%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETrigger%20warning%3A%20Mentions%20of%20suicide%2C%20bullying%2C%20eating%20disorder%20and%20depression%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20feeling%20of%20holding%20your%20child%20for%20the%20first%20time%20is%20indescribable.%20However%2C%20motherhood%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20first%20few%20months%2C%20can%20be%20challenging.%20It%20can%20have%20a%20significant%20impact%20on%20your%20mental%20health%20as%20you%20learn%20the%20art%20of%20taking%20care%20of%20a%20small%20human.%20Some%20mothers%20find%20pregnancy%20difficult%2C%20others%20have%20a%20traumatic%20labour%20and%20delivery%2C%20and%20some%20struggle%20during%20the%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F326043%2Ftwo-moms-serve-the-magic-of-home-cooked-eco-friendly-dabbas-to-thousands-in-london%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20postpartum%20period%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20Pooja%20Srinivasa%20Raja%2C%20it%20was%20the%20latter.%20After%20a%20smooth%20pregnancy%20and%20delivery%2C%20the%20then%2022-year-old%20was%20hit%20hard%20by%20postpartum%20depression.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20I%20felt%20had%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20my%20baby%20or%20the%20pregnancy%20or%20delivery.%20I%20felt%20very%20low.%20People%20would%20come%20and%20make%20unkind%20comments%20about%20my%20daughter%E2%80%99s%20appearance.%20They%20would%20say%20that%20she%20has%20a%20lot%20of%20facial%20hair%2C%20she%20is%20dark%2C%20etc.%20This%20really%20triggered%20me%20and%20reminded%20me%20of%20the%20trauma%20I%20went%20through%20growing%20up%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pooja%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPooja%20went%20through%20a%20very%20low%20phase%20for%20the%20first%20four%20months%20after%20childbirth.%20She%20recalls%20crying%20without%20a%20clear%20reason.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20just%20not%20okay.%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20feel%20like%20sleeping%2C%20and%20I%20was%20unsure%20about%20my%20career.%20Seeing%20my%20friends%20studying%20or%20working%20on%20social%20media%20led%20me%20further%20down%20the%20spiral.%20After%20three%20months%20postpartum%2C%20I%20started%20having%20suicidal%20thoughts%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20now%2027-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOne%20night%2C%20she%20poured%20out%20her%20feelings%20to%20her%20mother%20and%20cried.%20Her%20mother%20suggested%20that%20she%20should%20start%20therapy%2C%20which%20effectively%20turned%20around%20Pooja%E2%80%99s%20life.%20The%20therapy%20had%20such%20a%20transformational%20effect%20on%20this%20Chennai%20resident%E2%80%99s%20life%20that%20today%2C%20she%20runs%20a%20mental%20wellness%20startup%20called%20%E2%80%98The%20Love%20Hope%20Company%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20which%20she%20calls%20a%20%E2%80%98cafe%20for%20mental%20health%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLove%20and%20hope%20drive%20everything%20we%20do.%20We%20want%20to%20bring%20you%20a%20lot%20of%20love%20(self-love)%20and%20hope%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Pooja.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Therapy%20changed%20my%20life%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FLove-hope-company-1-1696427267.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Pooja%20started%20The%20Love%20Hope%20Company%2C%20a%20mental%20wellness%20space%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FLove-hope-company-1-1696427267.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FLove-hope-company-1-1696427267-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FLove-hope-company-1-1696427267-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.