he%20insisted%20I%20take%20an%20online%20session.%20It%20really%20helped.%20I%E2%80%99ve%20been%20able%20to%20realise%20many%20more%20things%20about%20myself%20and%20I%20am%20able%20to%20deal%20with%20my%20failures%20better.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPooja%20felt%20that%20there%20was%20still%20a%20lot%20of%20stigma%20around%20mental%20health.%20To%20bridge%20that%20gap%2C%20in%202019%2C%20she%20started%20an%20NGO%20called%20Transfomind%20Foundation%20%E2%80%94%20an%20online%20platform%20to%20create%20awareness%20of%20mental%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20collaborated%20with%20mental%20health%20experts%20to%20develop%20educational%20material%20on%20mental%20well-being.%20This%20idea%20gained%20traction%20during%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20raising%20significant%20awareness.%20In%20the%20second%20wave%20of%20the%20pandemic%2C%20we%20teamed%20up%20with%20Montfort%20College%20to%20offer%20free%20therapy%20sessions%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20businesswoman.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20also%20a%20challenging%20time%20in%20Pooja%E2%80%99s%20personal%20life%20as%20she%20was%20separated%20from%20her%20husband.%20During%20a%20solo%20trip%2C%20a%20conversation%20about%20the%20importance%20of%20mental%20health%20ignited%20the%20fire%20in%20the%2027-year-old%20to%20do%20something%20more%20concrete%20in%20the%20field.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20little%20bit%20of%20love%2C%20and%20a%20lot%20of%20hope%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FLove-hope-company-2-1696427268.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Group%20therapy%20spaces%20at%20The%20Love%20Hope%20Company%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FLove-hope-company-2-1696427268.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FLove-hope-company-2-1696427268-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FLove-hope-company-2-1696427268-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FLove-hope-company-2-1696427268-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FLove-hope-company-2-1696427268-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-331556%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EGroup%20therapy%20spaces%20at%20The%20Love%20Hope%20Company%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EMovies%20often%20give%20us%20a%20picture%20of%20a%20therapist%E2%80%99s%20office%20where%20the%20patient%20is%20just%20lying%20on%20a%20comfortable%20couch%20and%20talking%20about%20their%20feelings.%20In%20the%20real%20world%2C%20the%20setting%20is%20much%20more%20formal%20and%20clinical.%20To%20provide%20this%20comforting%20space%2C%20where%20one%20can%20express%20themselves%2C%20not%20just%20through%20words%2C%20but%20also%20through%20art%2C%20Pooja%20set%20up%20%E2%80%98The%20Love%20Hope%20Company%E2%80%99%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F325192%2Fsaakshi-gulati-nikita-mathur-travel-with-kids-india-plan-vacations-for-moms-kids-toddlers-baby%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emental%20wellness%20space%3C%2Fa%3E%20where%20we%20offer%20multiple%20services.%20We%20have%20counselling%20sessions%20for%20individuals%2C%20couples%2C%20families%2C%20and%20children.%20We%20have%20support%20groups%2C%20wellness%20workshops%20(where%20we%20use%20art%2C%20dance%20and%20drama%20to%20provide%20help)%20and%20group%20therapy%20sessions.%20We%20have%20designed%20our%20space%20to%20be%20one%20where%20people%20feel%20like%20opening%20up%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Pooja.%3C%2F