a%20circular%20economy%20in%20the%20kids%20category.%20The%20re-released%20products%20are%20in%20brand%20new%20quality%20and%20refurbishing%20the%20products%20help%20in%20increasing%20the%20products%20life%20by%20up%20to%2015%20years%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20bicycle%20subscription%20costs%20about%20Rs%206%2C000%20per%20year%20or%20Rs%20500%20per%20month%20while%20the%20cost%20of%20buying%20a%20bicycle%20can%20go%20as%20high%20as%20Rs%2020%2C000.%20Therefore%2C%20it%20is%20not%20only%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F311118%2Fpernod-richard-one-for-our-planet-initiative-encourages-sustainable-packaging-to-avoid-pollution%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eenvironmentally%20sustainable%3C%2Fa%3E%20but%20also%20cost-effective%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Pruthvi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20product%20of%20necessity%20and%20sustainability%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EProudly%20calling%20his%20household%20a%20%E2%80%9Csustainable%20family%E2%80%9D%2C%20Pruthvi%20feels%20that%20this%20lifestyle%20is%20the%20need%20of%20the%20hour.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBefore%20Gro%20Club%2C%20Pruthvi%20also%20started%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F224824%2Fbengaluru-startup-innovation-technology-convert-sewage-to-reusable-water-sustainable-india-gop94%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20tech-based%20startup%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20to%20bring%20a%20product%20in%20the%20market%20which%20was%20unique%20and%20sustainable%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWith%20Gro%20Club%2C%20we%20are%20able%20to%20reduce%20the%20increase%20in%20waste%20without%20curbing%20consumption%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Pruthvi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThey%20have%20a%20subscriber%20base%20of%205%2C700%20subscribers%20with%20an%20annual%20revenue%20of%20Rs%203%20