C%20the%20iconic%20eatery%20makes%20up%20to%20150%20kg%20of%20%3Cem%3Erabri%3C%2Fem%3E%20every%20day.%20Sold%20for%20two%20%3Cem%3Eanas%20%3C%2Fem%3E(Back%20then%2C%20anas%20were%20a%20form%20of%20currency%20and%2016%20anas%20makes%201%20Re)%20earlier%2C%20today%2C%20the%20sweet%20is%20sold%20for%20Rs%20500%20per%20kg.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20market%20rate%20of%20the%20sweet%20otherwise%20is%20Rs%20360-400%20per%20kg.%20Other%20than%20%3Cem%3Erabri%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20family%20introduced%20several%20traditional%20Rajasthani%20sweets%20like%20%3Cem%3Emoong%20thal%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Egulab%20chakri%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Ekalakand%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3Emaal%20puvey%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FMahaveer-Rabri-Bhandaar-1-1696338562.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20typical%20Rajasthani%20thali%20with%20bejad%20ki%20roti%2C%20aloo%20pyaaz%20paneer%20sabzi%2C%20gatte%20ki%20sabzi%2C%20dal%20tadka%2C%20mirchi%20ke%20Tipore%2C%20lehsun%20chutney%2C%20and%20raita.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FMahaveer-Rabri-Bhandaar-1-1696338562.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FMahaveer-Rabri-Bhandaar-1-1696338562-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FMahaveer-Rabri-Bhandaar-1-1696338562-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FMahaveer-Rabri-Bhandaar-1-1696338562-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FMahaveer-Rabri-Bhandaar-1-1696338562-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-331410%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EA%20